20represented%20Pasighat%20in%20the%20state%20assembly%20several%20times%20before%20winning%20the%20LS%20polls%20between%202009%20and%202019%2C%20would%20be%20able%20to%20stall%20the%20Congress%20from%20pocketing%20that%20seat%20in%20the%20coming%20polls.%20Ering%2C%20till%20yesterday%2C%20was%20the%20sitting%20Congress%20MLA%20from%20Pasighat.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20other%20Congress%20sitting%20MLA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farunachaltimes.in%2Findex.php%2F2024%2F02%2F26%2Fering-other-mlas-join-bjp%2F%5C%22%3Ewho%20defected%20to%20the%20BJP%20on%20February%2025%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20Wanglin%20Lowangdong.%20A%20graduate%20from%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20St%20Stephen%E2%80%99s%20College%2C%20Wanglin%20represented%20Congress%20in%20the%20outgoing%20assembly%20from%20Bordua%20Bogapani.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20state%20Congress%20called%20these%20defections%20the%20%E2%80%9Cpolitics%20of%20%3Cem%3Eaayaram%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3Egayaram%3C%2Fem%3E%20(people%20who%20come%20and%20go%20from%20parties)%E2%80%9D%20and%20urged%20the%20voters%20to%20reject%20such%20%E2%80%9Cseasonal%20and%20migratory%20political%20leaders%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAssam%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESimultaneously%2C%20similar%20movement%20of%20senior%20Congress%20leaders%20to%20the%20BJP%20in%20neighbouring%20Assam%20can%20also%20be%20seen.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20February%2025%2C%20Assam%20state%20Congress%20working%20president%20Rana%20Goswami%20resigned%20from%20the%20party.%20The%20buzz%20is%20that%20Goswami%2C%20a%20two-time%20MLA%20from%20the%20Jorhat%20constituency%2C%20will%20soon%20join%20BJP%2C%20now%20led%20by%20his%20former%20Congress%20colleague%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%202016%20and%202021%20assembly%20elections%2C%20Goswami%20had%20lost%20to%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Hitendra%20Nath%20Goswami.%3C%2F