Url%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Paytm%20FASTags%20Won't%20Work%20After%20March%2015%3A%20Check%205%20Alternatives%20Here%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPaytm%20Payments%20Bank%20Ltd%20(PPBL)%20has%20been%20removed%20from%20the%20list%20of%2032%20authorised%20banks%20for%20providing%20FASTag%20service.%20The%20move%20came%20amid%20the%20Reserve%20Bank%20Of%20India%20(RBI)%20giving%20the%20Paytm%20Payments%20Bank%20an%20extension%20to%20wind%20down%20its%20operations%20by%20March%2015%2C%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECustomers%20cannot%20top-up%20the%20existing%20FASTag%20after%20March%2015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20RBI%20issued%20a%20directive%20on%20January%2031%2C%20instructing%20PPBL%20to%20halt%20these%20financial%20activities.%20The%20extension%20comes%20as%20a%20relief%20for%20both%20Paytm%20Payments%20Bank%20and%20its%20customers%2C%20providing%20additional%20time%20for%20adjustments%20to%20be%20made.%20The%20central%20bank%20has%20not%20provided%20specific%20details%20on%20the%20reasons%20behind%20the%20extension.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20a%20FasTag%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EFasTag%20is%20an%20electronic%20toll%20collection%20system%20introduced%20in%20India%20to%20streamline%20and%20automate%20the%20toll%20payment%20process%20on%20highways.%20It%20utilises%20Radio-Frequency%20Identification%20(RFID)%20technology%20through%20a%20sticker%20or%20tag%20affixed%20to%20a%20vehicle's%20windshield.%20This%20tag%20is%20linked%20to%20the%20user's%20prepaid%20or%20savings%20account%2C%20allowing%20for%20automatic%20deduction%20of%20toll%20charges%20as%20the%20vehicle%20passes%20through%20equipped%20toll%20plazas.%20FasTag%20enhances%20the%20efficiency%20of%20toll%20collection%20by%20eliminating%20the%20need%20for%20manual%20payments%2C%20reducing%20travel%20time%2C%20and%20contributing%20to%20fuel%20savings.%20Its%20interoperable%20natu