0Shand%20-%20a%20Florida%20resident%20who%20was%20arrested%20in%202022%20after%20the%20bodies%20were%20recovered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPatel%20was%20part%20of%20an%20organised%20human%20smuggling%20group%20that%20facilitated%20illegal%20entry%20of%20Indian%20nationals%20into%20the%20United%20States%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20police%20said%20in%20its%20complaint.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20complaint%20also%20provides%20details%20of%20communication%20between%20Harshkumar%20Patel%20and%20Shand.%20They%20spoke%20about%20%26quot%3Barrangements%20for%20rental%20cars%2C%20hotels%2C%20and%20payments%20to%20Shand%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20one%20message%2C%20Patel%20told%20Shand%20to%20%26quot%3Bmake%20sure%20everyone%20is%20dressed%20for%20the%20blizzard%20conditions%20please%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShand%20described%20five%20total%20trips%20he%20had%20made%20to%20the%20international%20border%20in%20Minnesota%20between%20December%202021%20and%20January%202022%2C%20to%20transport%20Indian%20nationals%2C%20including%20the%20January%2019%2C%202022%20trip%20during%20which%20he%20was%20arrested%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20affidavit%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJagdish%20Baldevbhai%20Patel%2C%20his%20wife%20Vaishaliben%20Jagdishkumar%20Patel%20and%20their%20children%20Vihangi%20Jagdishkumar%20and%20Dharmik%20Jagdishkumar%20were%20found%20frozen%20to%20death%20near%20Emerson%2C%20Manitoba%20on%20January%2019%2C%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Patel%20family%20arrived%20in%20Toronto%20on%20January%2012%2C%202022%2C%20their%20first%20point%20of%20entry%20into%20Canada.%20From%20Toronto%2C%20the%20family%20made%20their%20way%20to%20Manitoba%20and%20eventually%20to%20Emerson%20before%20they%20died%20near%20the%20border%20due%20to%20exposure%20to%20extreme%20weather%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20had%20earlier%20said%20there%20was%20no%20abandoned%20vehicle%20located%20on%20the%20Canadian%20side%20of%20the%20border%2C%20clearly%20indicat