20shifted%20to%20PGIMER%20at%20Chandigarh%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20Mr%20Pandher%20said%20Pritpal%20Singh%20has%20suffered%20multiple%20injuries%20and%20condemned%20the%20police%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20farmer%20leader%20urged%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20to%20accept%20the%20demands%20of%20the%20protesters.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Prime%20Minister%20should%20also%20take%20action%20against%20policemen%20who%20indulge%20in%20such%20barbaric%20acts%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20action%20against%20the%20protesting%20farmers%20is%20set%20to%20turn%20into%20a%20flashpoint%20between%20Haryana%20and%20Punjab.%20The%20Bhagwant%20Mann%20government%20has%20already%20said%20%26quot%3Bappropriate%20legal%20action%20will%20be%20taken%20against%20the%20culprits%26quot%3B%20in%20Shubhkaran%20Singh's%20death.%20Punjab's%20Opposition%20parties%20have%20also%20reacted%20strongly%20to%20the%20farmer's%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECaptain%20Amarinder%20Singh's%20remarks%20on%20the%20injury%20to%20the%20farmer%20comes%20days%20after%20he%20met%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20discussed%20issues%20related%20to%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHad%20a%20detailed%20meeting%20with%20Hon'ble%20PM%20Shri%20Narendra%20Modi%20ji%20on%20wide-ranging%20issues%20related%20to%20Punjab%2C%20including%20the%20issues%20concerning%20the%20farmers%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20veteran%20leader%2C%20who%20was%20earlier%20with%20the%20Congress%2C%20said%20last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708928820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fia30v1ac_narendra-modi-amarinder-singh-ani_625x300_20_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Famarinder-singh-farmers-protest-amarinder-singh-slams-haryana-cops-over-injury-to-farmer-doing-langar-seva-5128965%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20the%20first%20such%20remark%20by%20any%20senior%20BJP%20leader%2C%20Captain%20Amarinder%20Singh%20ha