708925257000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108000231%2Cimgsize-576968.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fkolkata%2Ftmc-leader-shot-dead-in-west-bengal%2Farticleshow%2F108000119.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20CITY%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fkolkata%2Ftmc-leader-shot-dead-in-west-bengal%2Farticleshow%2F108000119.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Blame%20%E2%80%93%20and%20the%20Shame%20%E2%80%93%20of%20Three%20Million%20Bengali%20Dead%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F01%2F02211416%2FBengal_famine_1943.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Bengal%20countryside%20is%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20biggest%20archive%20in%20the%20world%E2%80%9D%2C%20comments%20a%20contributor%20to%20a%20new%20BBC%20audio%20series%2C%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fsounds%2Fbrand%2Fm001wr57%5C%22%3EThree%20Million%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%98.%20The%20wartime%20famine%20which%20claimed%20so%20many%20Bengali%20lives%20happened%20in%20plain%20sight.%20True%2C%20that%20was%2080%20years%20ago%2C%20and%20almost%20all%20eyewitnesses%20and%20survivors%20are%20now%20dead%3B%20but%20there%20are%20still%2C%20in%20all%20likelihood%2C%20thousands%20living%20with%20indelible%20memories%20of%20that%20trauma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%20there%20is%20no%20monument%20or%20memorial%20anywhere%20to%20all%20those%20who%20wasted%20away.%20The%20story%20has%20faded%20just%20as%20those%20subsisting%20on%20rice%20water%20slowly%20shrank%20to%20nothing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20333px)%2085vw%2C%20333px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F20115409%2Funnamed.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22333%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F20115409%2Funnamed.jpg%20526w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F20115409%2Funnamed-247x300.jpg%20247w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-649461%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22405%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bald%20geo-strategic%20facts%20are%20well%20established.%20As%20the%20Japanese%20army%20advanced%20deep%20into%20Burma%20in%201942%2C%20the%20war%20cabinet%20in%20London%20worried%20that%20Bengal%20too%20might%20fall%20to%20the%20enemy.%20The%20British%20authorities%20introduced%20a%20policy%20of%20%E2%80%98denial%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20destroying%20stocks%20of%20grain%20and%20the%20small%20boats%20so%20essential%20to%20Bengal%E2%80%99s%20economy%20lest%20they%20fall%20into%20Japanese%20hands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20no%20absolute%20food%20shortage%20%E2%80%93%20yet%20three%20million%2C%20some%20say%20more%2C%20starved%20to%20death.%20From%20the%20viceroy%E2%80%99s%20residence%2C%20Lord%20Wavell%20stormed%20about%20what%20he%20described%20as%20%E2%80%9Cone%20of%20the%20greatest%20disasters%20that%20had%20befallen%20any%20people%20under%20British%20rule%E2%80%9D%20with%20%E2%80%9Cincalculable%E2%80%9D%20damage%20to%20Britain%E2%80%99s%20reputation.%20But%20London%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20listening.%20And%20there%20were%20no%20spare%20ships%20to%20bring%20in%20emergency%20food%20supplies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWinston%20Churchill%2C%20Britain%E2%80%99s%20wartime%20prime%20minister%2C%20is%20often%20held%20to%20blame%20for%20the%20Bengal%20famine.%20This%20five-programme%20series%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20seek%20to%20convict%20him.%20But%20it%20does%20include%20telling%20testimony%20that%20in%20wartime%20he%20regarded%20the%20Empire%20as%20subordinate%20to%20the%20British%20homeland%2C%20and%20that%20he%20saw%20Indians%20as%20a%20sub-species.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlongside%20the%20blame%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20the%20shame.%20The%20British%20government%20must%20bear%20culpability.%20But%20it%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20Brits%20who%20hoarded%20the%20grain%2C%20took%20land%20from%20starving%20peasants%20in%20exchange%20for%20a%20small%20sack%20of%20rice%2C%20and%20bought%20young%20girls%20for%20a%20pittance%20for%20sex.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClass%20is%20another%20reason%20why%20the%20famine%20has%20been%20brushed%20away%20out%20of%20sight%20of%20the%20main%20historical%20narrative.%20If%20you%20were%20rich%2C%20you%20survived%20%E2%80%93%20there%20was%20food%20available%20if%20you%20could%20afford%20it.%20As%20ever%2C%20the%20poor%20and%20the%20marginalised%20bore%20the%20brunt%20%E2%80%93%20men%20often%20migrating%20to%20Calcutta%20and%20other%20towns%20in%20a%20desperate%20quest%20for%20work%20they%20were%20no%20longer%20strong%20enough%20to%20perform.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20257px)%2085vw%2C%20257px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F26103904%2FKavita-Puri-Jpeg.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22257%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F26103904%2FKavita-Puri-Jpeg.jpg%20448w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F26103904%2FKavita-Puri-Jpeg-210x300.jpg%20210w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-698847%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22367%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EKavita%20Puri.%20Photo%3A%20Special%20arrangement%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20astonishing%20success%20of%20%E2%80%98Three%20Million%E2%80%99%20is%20to%20present%20the%20famine%20as%20living%20history%20rather%20than%20a%20distant%20episode.%20It%E2%80%99s%20presented%20by%20Kavita%20Puri%2C%20one%20of%20the%20best%20documentary%20makers%20around.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20lived%20experience%20of%20the%20famine%20has%20not%20been%20well%20documented%20or%20remembered%2C%E2%80%9D%20Puri%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9Cand%20I%20wanted%20to%20recover%20these%20human%20stories.%E2%80%9D%20She%20does%20so%20with%20a%20sensitivity%20and%20compassion%20which%20never%20slips%20into%20shroud-waving%20sentimentality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPuri%20talks%20to%20the%20Nobel%20laureate%20Amartya%20Sen%2C%20then%20nine%20years%20old%20and%20living%20in%20Shanti%20Niketan%20and%20appalled%20by%20the%20emaciated%20people%20who%20passed%20by.%20%E2%80%9CHow%20much%20can%20I%20give%20them%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20asked%20his%20grandmother.%20The%20answer%3A%20just%20half%20a%20cigarette%20tin%20of%20grain%20a%20day.%20That%20memory%20shaped%20his%20life.%20Much%20of%20his%20academic%20career%20has%20been%20devoted%20to%20what%20causes%20famines%20and%20how%20they%20can%20be%20avoided.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPamela%20Dowley-Wise%2C%20born%20in%20Calcutta%20in%201926%2C%20saw%20%E2%80%9Cdead%20people%20all%20over%E2%80%9D%2C%20their%20carcasses%20preyed%20on%20by%20vultures.%20When%20the%20famine%20was%20at%20its%20most%20severe%2C%20as%20many%20as%20a%20thousand%20bodies%20a%20day%20were%20collected%20from%20Calcutta%E2%80%99s%20streets.%20The%20art%20historian%2C%20Partha%20Mitter%2C%20said%20that%20while%20his%20household%20had%20rice%20on%20the%20table%20every%20day%2C%20women%20would%20come%20to%20the%20gates%20pleading%20for%20a%20little%20of%20the%20water%20in%20which%20the%20rice%20was%20cooked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20tumult%20of%20war%2C%20the%20British%20authorities%20wanted%20to%20deflect%20attention%20from%20what%20they%20coyly%20described%20as%20the%20India%20food%20question.%20Ian%20Stephens%2C%20as%20editor%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3EStatesman%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20Calcutta%2C%20found%20a%20way%20around%20the%20wartime%20censorship.%20It%20applied%20to%20text%20not%20images.%20He%20sent%20his%20photographers%20onto%20the%20streets%20and%20on%20August%2022%2C%201943%2C%20he%20published%20harrowing%20images%20of%20famine%20victims%20at%20the%20point%20of%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%20the%20%3Cem%3EStatesman%20%3C%2Fem%3Enever%20named%20the%20starving%20men%20and%20women%20whose%20photographs%20it%20published.%20They%20were%20emblematic%20of%20humanity%20but%20denied%20their%20individual%20humanity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Chittaprosad%20Bhattacharya%E2%80%99s%20intensely%20powerful%20drawings%20of%20the%20starving%20were%20published%20as%20%3Cem%3EHungry%20Bengal%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%93%20a%20book%20promptly%20impounded%20by%20the%20colonial%20authorities%20%E2%80%93%20he%20was%20sure%20to%20give%20his%20subjects%20the%20dignity%20of%20a%20name.%20A%20drawing%20of%20a%20corpse%20in%20Midnapore%20being%20worried%20by%20a%20dog%20is%20captioned%3A%20%E2%80%9CHis%20name%20was%20Kshetramohan%20Naik%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20476px)%2085vw%2C%20476px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F26104817%2FChittaprosad-Hungry-Bengal-sketch1.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22476%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F26104817%2FChittaprosad-Hungry-Bengal-sketch1.jpeg%20389w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F26104817%2FChittaprosad-Hungry-Bengal-sketch1-300x197.jpeg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-698848%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22313%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EChittaprosad%20Bhattacharya%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98His%20name%20was%20Kshetramohan%20Naik%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BBC%20came%20under%20pressure%20at%20the%20time%20to%20downplay%20the%20gravity%20of%20the%20crisis.%20Puri%20uncovers%20evidence%20that%20it%20did%20indeed%20self-censor%20in%20its%20coverage%20of%20the%20famine.%C2%A0%20It%E2%80%99s%20taken%20an%20awfully%20long%20time%2C%20but%20these%20programmes%20at%20last%20make%20reparation%20for%20the%20BBC%E2%80%99s%20wartime%20failings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20extraordinary%20achievement%20of%20this%20series%20is%20in%20recovering%20the%20voices%20of%20some%20of%20the%20non-privileged.%20In%20Cambridge%2C%20Puri%20came%20across%20long%20forgotten%20recordings%20of%20veteran%20Indian%20civil%20servants%20made%20in%20the%201980s.%20And%20we%20hear%20from%20a%20school%20teacher%20in%20his%2070s%2C%20Sailen%20Sarkar%2C%20who%20has%20made%20it%20his%20mission%20to%20record%20the%20stories%20of%20village%20Bengalis%20who%20survived%20the%20famine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20series%20would%20be%20stronger%20with%20more%20raw%20testimony%20of%20those%20who%20suffered%20hunger%20pangs.%20Puri%20planned%20to%20accompany%20Sarkar%20on%20one%20of%20his%20journeys%20%E2%80%93%20but%20her%20visa%20application%20was%20never%20approved.%20She%20is%20still%20hoping%20to%20make%20it%20to%20West%20Bengal%20and%20meet%20survivors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20one%20positive%20consequence%20of%20the%20famine.%20Its%20impact%20persuaded%20the%20first%20generation%20of%20post-independence%20politicians%20to%20strive%20to%20ensure%20that%20famine%20would%20never%20again%20stalk%20their%20nation.%C2%A0%20Broadly%2C%20that%20goal%20has%20been%20met%3A%20there%20has%20been%20no%20major%20famine%20in%20India%20since%20independence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98Three%20Million%E2%80%99%20is%20available%20as%20a%20podcast%20from%20February%2023%20and%20will%20be%20broadcast%20on%20BBC%20World%20Service%20radio%20from%20March%202.%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAndrew%20Whitehead%20is%20a%20former%20BBC%20India%20correspondent.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3ELondon%20Calling%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0How%20does%20India%20look%20from%20afar%3F%20Looming%20world%20power%20or%20dysfunctional%20democracy%3F%20And%20what%E2%80%99s%20happening%20in%20Britain%2C%20and%20the%20West%2C%20that%20India%20needs%20to%20know%20about%20and%20perhaps%20learn%20from%3F%20This%20fortnightly%20column%20helps%20forge%20the%20connections%20so%20essential%20in%20our%20globalising%20world.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708925172000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F01%2F02211416%2FBengal_famine_1943.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fthe-blame-and-the-shame-of-three-million-bengali-dead%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20BBC%20audio%20series%20'Three%20Million'%20presents%20the%20famine%20as%20living%20history%20rather%20than%20a%20distant%20episode.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fthe-blame-and-the-shame-of-three-million-bengali-dead%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hindu%20Prayers%20To%20Continue%20In%20Gyanvapi%20Cellar%2C%20High%20Court%20Rejects%20Petition%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Allahabad%20High%20Court%20today%20dismissed%20a%20petition%20challenging%20the%20Varanasi%20district%20court's%20decision%20to%20allow%20Hindu%20prayers%20in%20a%20cellar%20of%20the%20Gyanvapi%20mosque.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHindu%20Prayers%20in%20the%20'Vyas%20Tehkhana'%20will%20continue%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Rohit%20Ranjan%20Agarwal%20said%20dismissing%20the%20mosque%20committee's%20petition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Varanasi%20district%20court%20had%20last%20month%20ruled%20that%20a%20priest%20can%20offer%20prayers%20in%20the%20southern%20cellar%20of%20the%20Gyanvapi%20mosque%20called%20%26quot%3BVyas%20Tehkhana%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20district%20court%20order%20was%20delivered%20on%20the%20petition%20of%20Shailendra%20Kumar%20Pathak%2C%20who%20said%20his%20maternal%20grandfather%20Somnath%20Vyas%20offered%20prayers%20till%20December%201993.%20Mr%20Pathak%20had%20requested%20that%2C%20as%20a%20hereditary%20pujari%2C%20he%20be%20allowed%20to%20enter%20the%20tehkhana%20and%20resume%20puja.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mosque%20has%20four%20'tehkhanas'%20(cellars)%20in%20the%20basement%2C%20and%20one%20of%20them%20is%20still%20with%20the%20Vyas%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mosque%20committee%20had%20refuted%20the%20petitioner's%20version.%20The%20committee%20said%20no%20idols%20existed%20in%20the%20cellar%2C%20so%20there%20was%20no%20question%20of%20prayers%20being%20offered%20there%20till%201993.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20committee%20went%20to%20the%20high%20court%20on%20February%202%20within%20hours%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20refusing%20to%20hear%20its%20plea%20against%20the%20Varanasi%20district%20court%20order%20and%20asking%20it%20to%20approach%20the%20high%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Allahabad%20High%20Court%20had%20reserved%20its%20order%20after%20hearing%20both%20parties%20on%20February%2015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20Archaeological%20Survey%20of%20India%20(ASI)%20report%20survey%2C%20ordered%20by%20the%20district%20court%2C%20in%20connection%20with%20a%20related%20case%2C%20had%20earlier%20suggested%20that%20the%20mosque%20was%20constructed%20during%20Aurangzeb's%20rule%20over%20the%20remains%20of%20a%20Hindu%20temple.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708925160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fllnc46hg_gyanvapi-mosque_625x300_03_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhindu-prayers-to-continue-in-gyanvapi-cellar-high-court-rejects-petition-challenging-varanasi-court-order-5128524%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Allahabad%20High%20Court%20today%20dismissed%20a%20petition%20challenging%20the%20Varanasi%20district%20court's%20decision%20to%20allow%20Hindu%20prayers%20in%20a%20cellar%20of%20the%20Gyanvapi%20mosque.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhindu-prayers-to-continue-in-gyanvapi-cellar-high-court-rejects-petition-challenging-varanasi-court-order-5128524%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhindu-prayers-to-continue-in-gyanvapi-cellar-high-court-rejects-petition-challenging-varanasi-court-order-5128524%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhindu-prayers-to-continue-in-gyanvapi-cellar-high-court-rejects-petition-challenging-varanasi-court-order-5128524%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Trinamool%20Leader%20Ajit%20Maity%20Arrested%20In%20Sandeshkhali%20Over%20Land%20Grab%20Charges%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20West%20Bengal%20Police%20arrested%20Trinamool%20Congress%20leader%20Ajit%20Maity%20from%20the%20trouble-torn%20Sandeshkhali%20in%20North%2024%20Parganas%20district%20on%20the%20charges%20of%20land%20grabbing%20from%20villagers%2C%20an%20officer%20said%20on%20Monday.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnAjit%20Maity%2C%20considered%20a%20close%20aide%20of%20absconding%20TMC%20strongman%20Shahjahan%20Sheikh%2C%20was%20detained%20on%20Sunday%20evening%20from%20the%20residence%20of%20a%20civic%20volunteer%20where%20he%20had%20locked%20himself%20for%20over%20four%20hours%20after%20being%20chased%20by%20villagers%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20arrested%20him%20after%20getting%20complaints%20from%20villagers%20regarding%20land%20grabbing.%20We%20will%20produce%20him%20in%20the%20court%20later%20in%20the%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20police%20officer%20told%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20getting%20over%2070%20complaints%2C%20the%20police%20lodged%20an%20FIR%20against%20Shajahan%20Shiekh%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20the%20complainants%20claimed%20that%20Shajahan%20was%20actively%20involved%20in%20the%20forcible%20acquisition%20of%20their%20land%20and%20torturing%20of%20local%20women%2C%20the%20police%20officer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAngry%20villagers%20had%20attacked%20Maity%20a%20couple%20of%20days%20back%20for%20his%20alleged%20ties%20with%20Shajahan%20and%20his%20group%2C%20accused%20of%20land%20grabbing%20and%20sexual%20assault%20on%20local%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20action%20comes%20after%20a%20TMC%20delegation%20visited%20the%20restive%20Sandeshkhali%20for%20the%20second%20consecutive%20day%20on%20Sunday%20and%20heard%20the%20grievances%20of%20villagers%20who%20have%20been%20protesting%20against%20alleged%20atrocities%20by%20local%20leaders%20of%20the%20ruling%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20riverine%20Sandeshkhali%20area%20--%20situated%20on%20the%20borders%20of%20the%20Sunderbans%2C%20about%20100%20kilometres%20from%20Kolkata%20--%20has%20been%20on%20the%20boil%20for%20more%20than%20a%20month%20with%20protests%20against%20Shahjahan%2C%20who%20is%20absconding%2C%20and%20his%20supporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708924920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fdq4b7qcg_sandeshkhali-ground-report_625x300_15_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fshahjahan-sheikh-trinamool-leader-ajit-maity-arrested-in-sandeshkhali-over-land-grab-charges-5128337%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20West%20Bengal%20Police%20arrested%20TMC%20leader%20Ajit%20Maiti%20from%20the%20trouble-torn%20Sandeshkhali%20in%20North%2024%20Parganas%20district%20on%20the%20charges%20of%20land%20grabbing%20from%20villagers%2C%20an%20officer%20said%20on%20Monday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fshahjahan-sheikh-trinamool-leader-ajit-maity-arrested-in-sandeshkhali-over-land-grab-charges-5128337%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fshahjahan-sheikh-trinamool-leader-ajit-maity-arrested-in-sandeshkhali-over-land-grab-charges-5128337%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fshahjahan-sheikh-trinamool-leader-ajit-maity-arrested-in-sandeshkhali-over-land-grab-charges-5128337%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BSparing%20Your%20Life%2C%20Go%20Tell%20His%20Family%2C%26quot%3B%20Killers%20Told%20INLD%20Leader's%20Nephew%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20nephew%20of%20Nafe%20Singh%20Rathi%20was%20at%20the%20wheel%20when%20the%20Indian%20National%20Lok%20Dal%20(INLD)%20leader%20was%20riddled%20with%20bullets%20last%20afternoon%20near%20a%20Railway%20crossing%20in%20Haryana's%20Jhajjar%20district.%20Rajesh%20has%20told%20police%20in%20his%20complaint%20that%20Mr%20Rathi%2C%20his%20maternal%20uncle%2C%20was%20sitting%20on%20the%20front%20left%20seat%2C%20right%20next%20to%20him%2C%20in%20the%20Toyota%20Fortuner%20SUV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rear%20seat%20was%20occupied%20by%20a%20gunner%20posted%20in%20the%2066-year-old%20INLD%20leader's%20security%20and%20a%20party%20colleague%2C%20Jaikishan%20Dalal.%20The%20SUV%20was%20waiting%20at%20the%20Barahi%20railway%20crossing%20on%20the%20way%20to%20Bahadurgarh%20when%20a%20car%20stopped%20behind%20it.%20Five%20men%20approached%20the%20SUV%20and%20fired%20at%20least%2020%20rounds%2C%20Rajesh%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20complaint%2C%20one%20of%20the%20shooters%20told%20Rajesh%20after%20the%20firing%20stopped%2C%20%26quot%3BTujhe%20zinda%20chor%20rahe%20hain%2C%20jake%20inke%20ghar%20bata%20diyo%20(we%20are%20sparing%20you%2C%20go%20and%20tell%20his%20family.)%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20basis%20of%20Rajesh's%20complaint%2C%20police%20have%20registered%20a%20case%20of%20murder%20against%20seven%20people%2C%20including%20BJP%20leader%20Naresh%20Kaushik%2C%20and%20several%20relatives%20of%20Bahadurgarh%20municipal%20corporation%20chaiperson%20Saroj%20Rathi.%20Charges%20of%20criminal%20conspiracy%20and%20Arms%20Act%20have%20also%20been%20slapped%20against%20the%20accused.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECCTV%20footage%20from%20the%20vicinity%20has%20shown%20an%20i20%20car%20tailing%20the%20SUV%20Mr%20Rathi%20was%20travelling%20in.%20The%20same%20camera%20has%20captured%20the%20car%20returning%20about%2020%20minutes%20later.%20Police%20suspect%20the%20killers%20came%20in%20this%20car.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20broad%20daylight%20shooting%20has%20sent%20shockwaves%20through%20Haryana%20and%20sparked%20criticism%20for%20the%20Manohar%20Lal%20Khattar%20government%20months%20ahead%20of%20the%20general%20and%20state%20elections.%20INLD%20leader%20Abhay%20Chautala%20has%20alleged%20that%20Mr%20Rathi%2C%20the%20party's%20Haryana%20chief%2C%20had%20asked%20for%20more%20security%20months%20back%2C%20but%20it%20was%20not%20provided.%20The%20Congress%20and%20AAP%2C%20too%2C%20have%20slammed%20the%20state%20government%20over%20the%20shocking%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNot%20a%20single%20culprit%20involved%20in%20this%20case%20will%20be%20spared.%20Police%20have%20been%20instructed%20to%20arrest%20the%20accused%20as%20soon%20as%20possible%20and%20take%20the%20strictest%20action%2C%26quot%3B%20Chief%20Minister%20Khattar%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708924800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F89pipllo_nafe-singh-rathi_625x300_26_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnafe-singh-rathi-nafe-singh-rathee-haryana-shooting-sparing-your-life-go-tell-his-family-killers-told-inld-leaders-nephew-5128700%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20nephew%20of%20Nafe%20Singh%20Rathi%20was%20at%20the%20wheel%20when%20the%20Indian%20National%20Lok%20Dal%20(INLD)%20leader%20was%20riddled%20with%20bullets%20last%20afternoon%20near%20a%20Railway%20crossing%20in%20Haryana's%20Jhajjar%20district%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnafe-singh-rathi-nafe-singh-rathee-haryana-shooting-sparing-your-life-go-tell-his-family-killers-told-inld-leaders-nephew-5128700%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnafe-singh-ra