s%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F03150954%2FPrism.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22300%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F03150954%2FPrism.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F03150954%2FPrism-150x150.png%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-691446%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22300%5C%22%3EIn%20May%20last%20year%2C%20while%20flagging%20off%20the%20Dehradun-Delhi%20Vande%20Bharat%20Express%2C%20the%20PM%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fpm-modi-slams-past-govts-real-work-to-change-rlys-started-after-2014-8629470%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edismissed%20all%20that%20the%20IR%20had%20achieved%20before%20his%20reign%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20by%20saying%20that%20parties%20in%20power%20before%202014%20made%20many%20promises%2C%20including%20on%20high-speed%20trains%2C%20but%20years%20went%20by%20without%20anything%20happening.%20He%20bragged%20that%20%E2%80%9Call-around%20work%20to%20transform%20the%20Railways%20began%20only%20after%202014%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20this%20comment%2C%20he%20belittled%20the%20invaluable%20contribution%20of%20railwaymen%20and%20women%20across%20the%20six-odd%20decades%20since%20independence.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20dishonesty%20at%20the%20top%20has%20percolated%20down%20and%20badly%20affected%20every%20aspect%20of%20government-working%2C%20including%20statistical%20bookkeeping%2C%20which%20is%20key%20not%20only%20to%20assessing%20performance%20but%20for%20taking%20major%20decisions.%20Today%2C%20government%20organisations%20are%20so%20mired%20in%20statistical%20fudging%20that%20most%20government-released%20data%20lack%20credibility.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAmidst%20this%20universal%20deceit%2C%20one%20recalls%20a%20time%20when%20our%20country%20was%20renowned%20for%20the%20authenticity%20of%20its%20statistics.%20A%20critical%20component%20of%20Chinese%20Premier%20Zhou%20Enlai%E2%80%99s%20visit%20to%20India%20in%201956%20was%20his%20interaction%20with%20a%20team%20of%20statisticians%20headed%20by%20the%20legendary%20P.C.%20Mahalanobis.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20from%20being%20a%20cutting-edge%20statistical%20powerhouse%2C%20the%20country%20has%20degenerated%20to%20a%20stage%20where%20our%20statistical%20figures%20are%20wishful%20rather%20than%20factual%20and%20increasingly%20at%20odds%20with%20the%20data%20and%20assessments%20of%20international%20rating%20agencies.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Frailway-narendra-modi-selfie-booth%5C%22%3ESmile%2C%20You%E2%80%99re%20With%20the%20PM%20and%20Your%20Train%20Isn%E2%80%99t%20on%20Time%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20IR%20has%20also%20been%20infected%20by%20this%20malaise.%20As%20a%20former%20railwayman%2C%20I%20know%20that%20the%20IR%20is%20sometimes%20cavalier%20about%20the%20statistics%20put%20out%20in%20the%20public%20domain%2C%20but%20this%20regime%20has%20gone%20over%20the%20top%20in%20manipulating%20statistics%2C%20mainly%20because%20of%20the%20ordained%20imperative%20of%20showing%20improvement%20in%20performance%20when%20compared%20with%20the%20position%20prior%20to%202014.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDespite%20the%20fog%20of%20secrecy%20and%20tight%20control%20over%20what%20information%20can%20be%20released%20for%20public%20consumption%2C%20the%20%E2%80%98doctoring%E2%80%99%20in%20some%20cases%20has%20come%20to%20light%20only%20because%20it%20is%20so%20brazen.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20average%20freight%20train%20speeds%20which%20were%2027.2%20kmph%20in%202010-11%20declined%20to%2024.4%20kmph%20in%202019-20%20but%20then%2C%20quite%20inexplicably%2C%20shot%20up%20to%2043.2%20kmph%20in%202020-21%20and%2037.3%20kmph%20in%202021-22%20by%20employing%20the%20simple%20artifice%20of%20deducting%20the%20period%20of%20major%20detentions%20enroute.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERegarding%20financial%20performance%2C%20even%20the%20otherwise%20pussy-footed%20Comptroller%20and%20Auditor%20General%20has%20pointed%20out%20the%20fudging%20of%20the%20operating%20ratio%20by%20removing%20pension%20expenditure%20appropriated%20to%20the%20pension%20fund%20from%20the%20computation%20of%20profitability.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELikewise%2C%20there%20is%20rigging%20in%20calculating%20the%20punctuality%20of%20trains%2C%20the%20duty%20hours%20of%20loco%20pilots%20and%20a%20lot%20else%20hidden%20behind%20the%20Railways%E2%80%99%20iron%20curtain%2C%20where%20officers%20cower%20in%20complicit%20silence.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20IR%20has%20historically%20been%20the%20mode%20of%20transport%20for%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eaam%20janta%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(common%20people)%20who%20have%20hitherto%20been%20the%20Railway%20management%E2%80%99s%20prime%20focus.%20The%20%E2%80%9Cvision%20statement%E2%80%9D%20of%202011-12%20stated%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9CIndian%20Railways%20shall%20provide%20safe%2C%20efficient%2C%20AFFORDABLE%2C%20customer-focussed%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%20transport%2C%20clearly%20spelling%20out%20its%20concern%20for%20the%20common%20person%20i.e.%20the%20second-class%20traveller.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20this%20regime%20is%20on%20an%20elitist%20binge%20with%20its%20energies%20and%20finances%20concentrated%20on%20spectacular%2C%20high-profile%20projects%20such%20as%20the%20Vande%20Bharat%20clutch%20of%20trains%2C%20the%20bullet%20train%20and%20profligate%20electrification.%20This%20lopsided%20fixation%20on%20glitzy%20projects%20has%20deflected%20managerial%20focus%20from%20the%20core%20areas%20associated%20with%20safety%2C%20such%20as%20maintenance%20and%20replacement%20of%20worn-out%20assets%20and%20upgrading%20safety%20infrastructure.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20glamorous%20Vande%20Bharat%20trains%20cater%20only%20to%20the%20well-heeled%2C%20reflected%20in%20the%20fact%20that%20whereas%20the%20cost%20of%20an%20ordinary%20second-class%20sleeper%20ticket%20by%20express%20train%20between%20Delhi%20and%20Kanpur%20is%20Rs%20300%2C%20the%20minimum%20fare%20by%20Vande%20Bharat%20is%20a%20whopping%20Rs%201%2C115.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fbalasore-odisha-train-clash-vande-bharat-modi-advertisement%5C%22%3ENeed%20For%20Speed%20Has%20Taken%20Focus%20off%20Rail%20Safety%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDespite%20protestations%20of%20concern%20for%20the%20most%20disadvantaged%20sections%2C%20the%20IR%20is%20replacing%20ordinary%20sleeper%20coaches%20from%20trains%20running%20at%20130%20kmph%20with%20AC-three-tier%20(economy)%20coaches%2C%20the%20fare%20of%20which%20is%20more%20than%20double%20the%20ordinary%20second-class%20fare.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20last%20few%20years%2C%20no%20new%20Jan%20Shatabdi%20train%2C%20which%20caters%20mainly%20to%20the%20second-class%20passenger%20segment%2C%20has%20been%20introduced.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20brutal%20capitalistic%20ethic%20reigns%20behind%20the%20veneer%20of%20%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Esabka%20saath%20sabka%20vikas%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%99%20socialism.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20railway%20minister%20constantly%20harps%20on%20how%20the%20Railways%20in%20this%20regime%E2%80%99s%20watch%20has%20seen%20real%20transformation%2C%20a%20radical%20reformation%20of%20systems.%20But%20the%20havoc%20wreaked%2C%20apparently%20on%20the%20ill-conceived%20advice%20of%20a%20cabal%20of%20pet%20consultants%2C%20could%20more%20appropriately%20be%20described%20as%20institutional%20bombing%20that%20has%20undone%20systems%20and%20structures%20developed%20and%20nurtured%20over%20the%20decades.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20guys%20are%20fecklessly%20advocating%20change%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20change%2C%20oblivious%20to%20the%20damaging%20effects%20on%20the%20system.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETake%20the%20merger%20of%20the%20Railway%20Budget%20with%20the%20Union%20Budget%20in%202016%2C%20disregarding%20the%20compelling%20rationale%20that%20the%20Railways%20needed%20to%20be%20independent%2C%20nimble-footed%20in%20decision-making%20and%20insulated%20from%20the%20rigid%20bureaucratic%20practices%20that%20typify%20government%20working.%20A%20catastrophic%20consequence%20of%20the%20institutional%20degradation%20has%20been%20a%20loss%20of%20focus%20on%20financial%20performance%20and%20balancing%20profitability%20with%20social%20obligations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20the%20subsuming%20of%20the%20Railway%20Budget%20into%20the%20General%20Budget%2C%20public%20oversight%20and%20scrutiny%20of%20our%20leading%20carrier%20is%20also%20no%20longer%20possible%20and%20that%20suits%20a%20regime%20that%20thrives%20on%20cloak-and-dagger%20functioning.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnother%20radical%20but%20disastrous%20decision%20is%20the%20total%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fin-major-revamp-government-clears-merger-of-8-railway-services%2Farticleshow%2F72960884.cms%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Erevamp%20of%20the%20railway%20management%20structure%20in%202019%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20based%20on%20a%20half-baked%20understanding%20of%20the%20complexities%20of%20the%20Railways.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20wholesale%20%E2%80%9Chomogenisation%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20management%20cadre%20was%20done%20to%20combat%20departmentalism%2C%20a%20term%20coined%20to%20describe%20the%20rivalry%20and%20hostility%20between%20departments%20within%20the%20Railways%2C%20but%20what%E2%80%99s%20been%20done%20is%20akin%20to%20burning%20down%20a%20house%20to%20smoke%20out%20a%20rat.%20Almost%20five%20years%20on%2C%20the%20ministry%20is%20still%20floundering%20on%20the%20rules%20regarding%20recruitment%2C%20seniority%20and%20appointment%20to%20key%20positions.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fwhy-the-railways-figures-spell-doom-for-economy-passengers%5C%22%3EWhy%20the%20Railways%E2%80%99%20Figures%20Spell%20Doom%20for%20Economy%20Passengers%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20most%20disturbing%20spin-off%20from%20this%20god%20awful%20mess%20is%20the%20fishy%20new%20method%20of%20selection%20to%20the%20top%20managerial%20positions.%20The%20traditional%2C%20time-tested%20system%20of%20assessment%20based%20on%20record%20of%20service%20as%20reflected%20in%20the%20annual%20confidential%20reports%20twinned%20with%20vigilance%20clearance%20regarding%20integrity%20has%20been%20given%20the%20heave-ho%20in%20favour%20of%20an%20AB%20De%20Villiers-like%20%E2%80%9C360-degree%E2%80%9D%20assessment%20which%2C%20like%20the%20great%20South%20African%E2%80%99s%20pyrotechnics%2C%20observes%20no%20rules.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202022%2C%20using%20the%20crutch%20of%20merit%20in%20lieu%20of%20the%20time-tested%20system%20of%20seniority-cum-suitability%20based%20selection%2C%20the%20ministry%20chose%20only%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fonly-8-of-130-in-fray-picked-for-irms-cadre-railway-gm-posts-8255298%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eeight%20officers%20from%20a%20pool%20of%20130%20aspirants%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20for%20the%20coveted%20post%20of%20general%20manager.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFactored%20into%20the%20selection%20was%20an%20assessment%20of%20the%20candidates%20by%20an%20establishment-preferred%20group%20of%20retired%20bureaucrats%20who%20played%20Solomon%2C%20apart%20from%20subjecting%20the%20candidates%20to%20a%20dubious%20psycho-analytical%20test%20to%20assess%20their%20%E2%80%9Cemotional%20quotient%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%E2%80%99s%20obvious%20is%20that%20this%20highfalutin%20procedure%20is%20a%20mere%20crutch%20for%20the%20powers-that-be%20to%20choose%20whomsoever%20they%20want%20in%20the%20top%20managerial%20positions.%20Never%20has%20the%20morale%20of%20Railway%20officials%20been%20as%20low%20as%20it%20is%20today.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20conclusion%2C%20one%20cannot%20help%20taking%20note%20of%20how%20unrestrained%20this%20regime%20has%20been%20in%20its%20psychotic%20eagerness%20to%20erase%2C%20diminish%20or%20appropriate%20whatever%20was%20achieved%20before%202014.%20Even%20the%20Railways%E2%80%99%20invaluable%20heritage%20has%20not%20been%20spared.%20In%20the%20war%20with%20the%20past%2C%20culturally%20evocative%20artefacts%20and%20institutions%20have%20been%20uprooted%20to%20make%20way%20for%20newfangled%20replacements%20associated%20with%20this%20regime.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20iconic%20Darjeeling%20Hill%20Railway%20(DHR)%20steam%20locomotive%20of%201925%20vintage%2C%20which%20for%20decades%20adorned%20the%20front%20of%20the%20Rail%20Bhawan%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20was%20shunted%20out%20to%20the%20Rail%20Museum%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fheritage-steam-loco-removed-from-rail-bhawan-vande-bharat-replica-to-replace-it%2Farticleshow%2F88129614.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereplaced%20with%20a%20Vande%20Bharat%20replica%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20what%20has%20traumatised%20Railwaymen%20past%20and%20present%20has%20been%20the%20uprooting%20of%20the%20Railway%20Staff%20College%20in%20Vadodara%20%E2%80%93%20renamed%20the%20National%20Academy%20of%20Indian%20Railways%20(NAIR)%20%E2%80%93%20which%2C%20since%201952%2C%20has%20been%20the%20seat%20of%20learning%20for%20officers%20of%20the%20IR.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20few%20weeks%20ago%2C%20the%20ministry%20directed%20the%20NAIR%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fnational-academy-of-indian-railways-told-to-hand-over-assets-to-gati-shakti-vishwavidyalaya%2Farticle67658364.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehand%20over%20all%20its%20assets%20to%20the%20Gati%20Shakti%20Vidyalaya%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(GSV)%2C%20a%20%E2%80%98Central%20University%20envisioned%20by%20PM%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20one%20fell%20sweep%2C%20an%20institution%20of%20learning%2C%20steeped%20in%20railway%20lore%20and%20culture%2C%20has%20been%20expelled%20to%20make%20way%20for%20yet%20another%20highfalutin%20vanity%20project%20of%20the%20authoritarian.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20leading%20historian%20has%20observed%20that%20while%20history%20is%20in%20the%20past%2C%20heritage%20is%20in%20the%20present.%20It%20provides%20a%20visceral%20link%20with%20the%20spirit%20of%20the%20past%20and%20helps%20inspire%20a%20better%20perspective%20and%20understanding%20of%20our%20present.%20Or%20to%20modify%20what%20Marcus%20Garvey%20said%2C%20an%20institution%20without%20knowledge%20of%20its%20history%2C%20origin%20and%20culture%20is%20like%20a%20tree%20without%20roots.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20the%20philistines%20who%20call%20the%20shots%20today%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20care%20less%20for%20such%20soulful%20niceties.%20For%20them%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20all%20about%20one%20man%20and%20his%20image!%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fmathew-john%5C%22%3EMathew%20John%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20former%20civil%20servant.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708911036000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.