%20RLD%20led%20by%20Jayant%20Chaudhary.%20Amidst%20the%20rumours%20of%20Jayant%20Chaudhry%E2%80%99s%20disgruntlement%20with%20the%20seat%20sharing%20in%20NDA%2C%20two%20significant%20questions%20have%20come%20up%3A%20what%20prompted%20the%20SP-Congress%20alliance%20in%20UP%2C%20and%20what%20can%20it%20achieve%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EElectoral%20compulsions%20and%20ideological%20similarities%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrying%20to%20recover%20from%20the%20election%20debacles%20in%20the%202022%20assembly%20and%20later%20urban%20body%20elections%2C%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20coined%20the%20formula%20of%20a%20PDA%20%E2%80%93%20%3Cem%3EPichda%2C%20Dalit%2C%20Alpasankhyak%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Backwards%2C%20Dalits%2C%20Minorities)%20alliance.%20While%20voting%20patterns%20of%20past%20elections%20show%20that%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20and%20its%20allies%20still%20command%20a%20sizeable%20share%20of%20votes%20of%20non-Yadav%20OBCs%20and%20non-Jatav%20Dalits%20in%20UP%2C%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20realised%20that%20there%20is%20a%20significant%20section%20of%20these%20communities%20who%20are%20getting%20disenchanted%20with%20the%20BJP.%20Factors%20like%20agrarian%20issues%2C%20inflation%20and%20joblessness%20among%20these%20communities%20were%20considered%20to%20be%20the%20major%20forces%20behind%20this.%20Accordingly%2C%20the%20party%20prepared%20a%20strategy%20to%20reach%20out%20to%20these%20communities%20at%20the%20booth%20level%20and%20establish%20a%20direct%20connect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWorking%20on%20similar%20lines%20albeit%20much%20earlier%20and%20on%20an%20all-India%20level%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20first%20launched%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%20and%20later%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%20to%20galvanise%20anti-BJP%20sentiment%20among%20these%20communities.%20%E2%80%9CCongress%20has%20been%20consistently%20raising%20the%20issue%20of%20caste%20census%2C%20socio-economic%20justice%20and%20joblessness.%20The%20two%20yatras%20of%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20have%20attempted%20to%20make%20the%20Dalit-OBC%20population%20of%20the%20country%20realise%20that%20their%20future%20is%20not%20safe%20with%20the%20BJP%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20UP%20Congress%20general%20secretary%20Anil%20Yadav.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Congress-SP%20Alliance%20Seals%20Seat-Sharing%20Deal%20in%20UP%20and%20MP%2C%20but%20Some%20Major%20Challenges%20Remain%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcongress-sp-alliance-seals-seat-sharing-deal-in-up-and-mp-but-some-major-challenges-remain%5C%22%3ECongress-SP%20Alliance%20Seals%20Seat-Sharing%20Deal%20in%20UP%20and%20MP%2C%20but%20Some%20Major%20Challenges%20Remain%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20SP%20succeed%20in%20getting%20majority%20of%20Muslim%20and%20Yadav%20votes%20in%202022%20as%20per%20CSDS%20data%2C%20it%20was%20not%20so%20successful%20in%20attracting%20Dalit%20and%20other%20OBC%20voters%2C%20due%20to%20it%20being%20seen%20as%20a%20Muslim-Yadav%20party.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20past%20surveys%20done%20by%20People%E2%80%99s%20Pulse%20in%20UP%20indicate%20that%20despite%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%E2%80%99s%20positive%20image%2C%20these%20communities%20did%20not%20vote%20for%20the%20Congress%20due%20to%20the%20perception%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20in%20the%20fight%20in%20the%20bi-polar%202022%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWith%20both%20parties%20now%20coming%20together%20in%20an%20alliance%2C%20these%20shortcomings%20could%20be%20overcome.%20While%20the%20Congress%20can%20soften%20the%20image%20of%20the%20SP%20and%20widen%20the%20vote%20base%20of%20the%20party%2C%20the%20SP%20can%20increase%20the%20winnability%20perception%20of%20the%20former%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Lucknow-based%20veteran%20journalist%20Siddharth%20Kalhans.%20It%20is%20also%20to%20be%20noted%20that%20the%202022%20surveys%20indicated%20that%20a%20majority%20of%20Muslim%20voters%20were%20clearly%20saying%20that%20though%20in%202022%20they%20are%20voting%20for%20the%20Mahagathbandhan%2C%20they%20will%20vote%20for%20the%20Congress%20in%202024.%20The%20SP%20was%20wary%20of%20losing%20them%20in%20a%20crucial%20election%20like%202024.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20therefore%20seems%20that%20electoral%20compulsions%20and%20similar%20ideological%20goals%20perhaps%20brought%20the%20two%20parties%20together%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20sums%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20can%20the%20alliance%20achieve%20in%20UP%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%2C%20while%20passing%20through%20UP%2C%20attracted%20huge%20crowds%20and%20was%20joined%20by%20SP%20leaders%20and%20cadres%20alike.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20incumbent%20UP%20government%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fup-police-recruitment-exam-cancelled-bjp-yields-to-pressure-amid-paper-leak-allegations-protests%5C%22%3Eis%20facing%20the%20ire%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20unemployed%20youth%20protesting%20against%20paper%20leaks%20in%20constable%20and%20RO%2FARO%20recruitment%20exams.%20Amidst%20these%20developments%2C%20some%20experts%20feel%20that%20the%20euphoria%20and%20positive%20atmosphere%20that%20the%20BJP%20created%20through%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20inauguration%20in%20early%20January%20seems%20to%20be%20subsiding.%20But%20will%20this%20mean%20that%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20can%20properly%20challenge%20the%20NDA%20in%202024%20in%20UP%2C%20bringing%20down%20its%20numbers%20from%2064%20(62%20to%20BJP%20and%20two%20to%20Apna%20Dal%20Sonelal)%20in%202019%3F%20A%20closer%20look%20at%20the%20data%20of%20past%20elections%20and%20current%20trends%20might%20give%20us%20a%20clearer%20picture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20general%20understanding%20is%20that%20the%20vote%20share%20of%20the%20Mahagathbandhan%20led%20by%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20in%20the%202022%20assembly%20election%20was%20more%20than%2038.5%25%2C%20if%20we%20include%20the%20Congress.%20This%20amounts%20to%20approximately%2030%20out%20of%2080%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20the%20state.%20However%2C%20vote%20percentage%20alone%20does%20not%20amount%20to%20seats%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20first-past-the-post%20system.%20A%20party%20could%20be%20getting%20votes%20across%20a%20state%20which%20might%20look%20impressive%20in%20total%2C%20and%20yet%20fail%20to%20win%20a%20single%20seat.%20The%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%E2%80%99s%20performance%20in%20UP%20during%20the%202014%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20is%20a%20classic%20example%20of%20this%2C%20as%20the%20party%20failed%20to%20win%20a%20single%20seat%20despite%20polling%2019.77%25%20of%20the%20total%20votes.%20In%20this%20scenario%2C%20the%20seats%20won%2Fleads%20logic%20appears%20more%20appropriate%20to%20make%20a%20projection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22The%20India%20Alliance%20May%20Not%20Be%20as%20Dead%20After%20All%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fthe-india-alliance-may-not-be-as-dead-after-all%5C%22%3EThe%20India%20Alliance%20May%20Not%20Be%20as%20Dead%20After%20All%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20terms%20of%20seats%20won%20in%20the%20assembly%2C%20the%20Mahagathbandhan%20(including%20the%20Congress)%20collectively%20led%20in%20127%20assembly%20segments%20which%20also%20roughly%20converts%20to%20around%2025%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20(as%20one%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20is%20made%20of%20five%20assembly%20seats%20in%20UP%2C%20generally).%20By%20this%20logic%2C%20the%20NDA%20could%20be%20limited%20to%20around%2055%20seats%20in%20the%202024%20elections%20by%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%2C%20which%20is%20far%20less%20than%20the%2064%20it%20won%20in%202019.%20But%20in%20the%202022%20assembly%20election%2C%20the%20BJP%20contested%20in%20alliance%20with%20the%20Apna%20Dal%20and%20Nishad%20Party%20only%2C%20and%20now%20it%20also%20has%20the%20support%20of%20the%20SBSP%20and%20RLD%2C%20who%20jumped%20sides%20after%20the%20elections.%20Adding%20their%20numbers%20to%20the%20NDA%20seat%20tally%20of%202022%20results%20in%20the%20saffron%20alliance%20jumping%20to%20287%20seats%2C%20which%20amounts%20to%20around%2058%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20can%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20limit%20the%20BJP%20to%20even%20those%20numbers%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENarrative%2C%20social%20engineering%20and%20political%20churn%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20shortcomings%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20currently%20the%20most%20prepared%20party%20for%20the%20upcoming%20elections%2C%20with%20enormous%20organisational%20and%20government%20machinery%20and%20huge%20financial%20resources%20at%20its%20disposal.%20Major%20surveys%20show%20that%20though%20the%20popularity%20of%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20has%20increased%2C%20that%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20is%20still%20unmatchable.%20Further%2C%20its%20narrative%20of%20%E2%80%9CRam%2C%20Roti%20and%20Rashtra%E2%80%9D%20(Hindutva%2C%20beneficiary%20policies%20and%20hyper%20nationalism)%20has%20still%20not%20lost%20its%20shine%2C%20despite%20the%20opposition%E2%80%99s%20attempts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%20in%20UP%2C%20it%20has%20always%20been%20a%20battle%20between%20social%20engineering%20and%20narrative.%20And%20the%20SP-Congress%20alliance%20seems%20to%20have%20taken%20the%20first%20step%20to%20carve%20out%20a%20greater%20social%20base%2C%20charged%20with%20an%20anti-BJP%20narrative.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20has%20been%2012%20years%20since%20the%20BSP%20lost%20power%20in%20UP%20and%20it%20has%20not%20recovered%20since%20then%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dr%20Rama%20Shankar%2C%20a%20fellow%20at%20Ambedkar%20University%20Delhi%20and%20the%20author%20of%20a%20book%20on%20UP%E2%80%99s%20EBCs.%20%E2%80%9CA%20large%20section%20of%20the%20BSP%20vote%20base%20%E2%80%93%20Dalits%20and%20EBCs%20%E2%80%93%20which%20was%20disgruntled%20is%20definitely%20available%20and%20trying%20to%20find%20new%20political%20options.%E2%80%9D%20However%2C%20he%20also%20cautions%20that%20the%20voting%20memory%20of%20these%20groups%20for%20Congress%20is%20very%20old%20and%20they%20have%20not%20liked%20the%20SP%20due%20to%20a%20history%20of%20social%20conflicts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20the%20above%20factors%2C%20what%20the%20SP-Congress%20alliance%20will%20achieve%20will%20greatly%20depend%20on%20the%20right%20messaging%2C%20better%20candidates%20and%20creating%20a%20larger%20social%20base.%20With%20a%20freefall%20in%20BSP%E2%80%99s%20situation%20in%20UP%20and%20its%20absence%20from%20all%20major%20political%20interventions%20and%20issues%2C%20various%20social%20blocs%20and%20castes%20previously%20loyal%20to%20it%20are%20looking%20for%20options.%20If%20the%20SP-Congress%20alliance%20succeeds%20in%20creating%20a%20broadened%20social%20base%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20possible%20for%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20to%20at%20least%20stop%20the%20BJP%20from%20gaining%20in%20UP%20above%20the%202019%20numbers%20%E2%80%93%20and%20even%20that%20would%20be%20no%20small%20achievement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ERajan%20Pandey%20is%20a%20freelance%20journalist.%20He%20is%20also%20associated%20with%20Hyderabad-based%20survey%20agency%20People%E2%80%99s%20Pulse.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708871455000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F25161348%2FGHLSQf0aYAAENH-.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwhat-might-the-congress-samajwadi-party-alliance-achieve-in-uttar-pradesh%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22What%20the%20SP-Congress%20alliance%20will%20achieve%20will%20greatly%20depend%20on%20the%20right%20messaging%2C%20better%20candidates%20and%20creating%20a%20larger%20social%20base.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwhat-might-the-congress-samajwadi-party-alliance-achieve-in-uttar-pradesh%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20pictures%3A%20Celebrating%20the%20Lantern%20Festival%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708868594000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F10895%2Fproduction%2F_132733776_b6aca753b0472fbc1ef4d34d8f5c4eab62ae6fb60_127_5906_37541000x636.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-68397159%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20festival%20marks%20the%20end%20of%20Lunar%20New%20Year%20festivities%20-%20this%20year%20is%20Year%20of%20the%20Dragon.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A391%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-68397159%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-68397159.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-68397159.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22BJP%20in%20Tight%20Spot%20Over%20Fresh%20Round%20of%20Farmers%20Protest%2C%20Reconciliation%20With%20Akali%20Dal%20on%20Back%20Burner%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F27210340%2FEffect.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EChandigarh%3A%20At%20a%20time%20when%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20was%20trying%20to%20regain%20electoral%20support%20in%20Punjab%20after%20the%20farmers%20protest%20in%202020%2C%20another%20round%20of%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest%20has%20increased%20its%20worries%20ahead%20of%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EThe%20recent%20crackdown%20by%20the%20BJP-led%20Haryana%20government%20to%20prevent%20farmers%20from%20reaching%20Delhi%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Ffarmers-protest-haryana-police-shubhkaran-singh%5C%22%3Efollowed%20by%20the%20death%20of%20a%20young%20farmer%2C%20Shubhkaran%20Singh%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20has%20only%20worsened%20the%20situation%20for%20the%20party%20which%2C%20until%20recently%2C%20was%20confident%20of%20performing%20well%20on%20Punjab%E2%80%99s%2013%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EAs%20per%20poll%20observers%2C%20the%20biggest%20setback%20for%20BJP%20is%20the%20pause%20on%20talks%20for%20a%20potential%20alliance%20with%20the%20Shiromani%20Akali%20Dal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EThe%20Akali%20Dal%2C%20which%20primarily%20thrives%20on%20rural%20vote%20bank%2C%20was%20forced%20to%20break%20ties%20with%20the%20BJP%20after%20the%20latter%20passed%20passed%20three%20central%20farm%20laws%20in%202020%2C%20which%20farmers%20saw%20a%20direct%20dilution%20of%20minimum%20support%20price%20(MSP)%20system%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EThis%20triggered%20the%20protest%20among%20Punjab%E2%80%99s%20peasantry%2C%20as%20well%20as%20farmers%20of%20other%20states%2C%20who%20had%20to%20camp%20on%20Delhi%20borders%20for%20over%20a%20year%20before%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fthree-controversial-farm-laws-will-be-repealed-narendra-modi-announces%23%3A~%3Atext%3DHundreds%2520of%2520farmers%2520have%2520been%2CAct%252C%25202020%253B%2520and%2520the%2520Essential%5C%22%3EUnion%20government%20withdrew%20the%20bills.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EIn%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20protest%2C%20the%20BJP%20secured%20just%20a%20little%20over%206%25%20of%20the%20votes%20during%20the%202022%20Punjab%20Assembly%20polls%2C%20while%20the%20performance%20of%20the%20Akali%20Dal%20also%20hit%20an%20all-time%20low.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EIn%20the%20two%20Lok%20Sabha%20by-polls%20held%20since%20then%2C%20the%20BJP%20candidates%20had%20to%20forfeit%20their%20security%20deposit%20%E2%80%93%20a%20clear%20sign%20of%20party%E2%80%99s%20unpopularity%20in%20the%20state%20it%20once%20ruled%20in%20alliance%20with%20the%20Akali%20Dal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EWith%20no%20apparent%20sign%20of%20revival%20for%20the%20Akali%20Dal%2C%20both%20sides%20had%20begun%20talks%20of%20rekindling%20their%20alliance%20for%20mutual%20survival%20with%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20recently%20dropping%20a%20hint%C2%A0that%20talks%20were%20on%20with%20SAD.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EJust%20when%20both%20the%20parties%20thought%20that%20the%20ghost%20of%20the%202020%20farmers%20protest%20was%20behind%20them%20and%20they%20could%20revive%20their%20tried%20and%20tested%20urban-rural%20vote%20bank%20combination%2C%20another%20round%20of%20farm%20protest%20has%20created%20fresh%20hurdles%20in%20their%20reconciliation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EThis%20is%20evident%20from%20the%20current%20posturing%20of%20Akali%20Dal%2C%20which%20has%20completely%20tilted%20towards%20the%20cause%20of%20farmers%2C%20their%20core%20base%2C%20since%20the%20Delhi%20Chalo%20demonstration%20began%20on%20February%2013.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EAkali%20Dal%20leaders%20have%20been%20attacking%20both%20BJP%20as%20well%20as%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20governments%2C%20in%20Haryana%20and%20Punjab%20respectively%2C%20over%20the%20ongoing%20protests%20currently%20stuck%20at%20Punjab-Haryana%20borders%20in%20Shambhu%20and%20Khanari.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EWhile%20five%20farmers%20have%20died%20so%20far%2C%20nearly%20200%20have%20been%20injured%20in%20clashes%20with%20Haryana%20police%20which%20is%20heavily%20guarding%20the%20state%20borders%20to%20prevent%20farmers%20from%20reaching%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EPolitical%20analyst%20Pramod%20Kumar%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20although%20the%20alliance%20is%20very%20important%20for%20the%20political%20survival%20of%20both%20BJP%20and%20SAD%20in%20Punjab%2C%20the%20possibility%20of%20such%20alliance%20looks%20difficult%20at%20the%20moment.%20The%20parties%20will%20only%20be%20able%20to%20join%20hands%20if%20the%20protest%20ends%20or%20taken%20to%20a%20logical%20conclusion.%20Whether%20or%20not%20it%20this%20will%20happen%20depends%20upon%20future%20negotiations%20between%20the%20Union%20government%20and%20the%20protesting%20farmers%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EAs%20per%20information%2C%20talks%20between%20the%20Union%20government%20and%20farmers%20are%20on%20hold%20ever%20since%20the%20death%20of%20Shubkaran%20Singh%20last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EBoth%20sides%20held%20four%20round%20of%20talks%20but%20failed%20to%20break%20a%20deadlock%20on%20one%20key%20demand%20regarding%20an%20MSP%20guarantee%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EUnion%20agriculture%20minister%20Arjun%20Munda%20recently%20invited%20farmer%20leaders%20for%20another%20round%20of%20talks%20but%20there%20is%20no%20response%20from%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20side%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EThe%20protest%20has%20also%20been%20paused%20till%20February%2029%20in%20wake%20of%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20death.%20Sarwan%20Singh%20Pandher%20and%20Jagjit%20Dallewal%2C%20who%20are%20leading%20the%20protest%2C%20told%20the%20media%20on%20Saturday%20that%20they%20would%20decide%20their%20next%20course%20of%20action%20during%20a%20common%20meeting%20with%20all%20farmer%20unions%20on%20February%2028.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EPunjab%20BJP%20leaders%20break%20silence%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EPreviously%20silent%20on%20the%20matter%2C%20Punjab%20BJP%20leaders%20have%20now%20begun%20voicing%20their%20support%20for%20an%20early%20resolution%20between%20farmers%20and%20the%20Union%20government.%20They%20also%20criticised%20the%20Haryana%20police%E2%80%99s%20action%20on%20protesting%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EPunjab%20BJP%20chief%20Sunil%20Jakhar%20condemned%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20death%20and%20even%20demanded%20through%20investigation%20via%20a%20post%20on%20Facebook%20on%20Friday.%C2%A0He%20asked%20for%20the%20%E2%80%9Cgovernments%20and%20security%20forces%20to%20observe%20restraints%20and%20sensitivity%20to%20allow%20peaceful%20protests%E2%80%9D%2C%20which%20many%20see%20as%20an%20indirect%20attack%20on%20his%20own%20party%E2%80%99s%20government%20in%20Haryana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EJakhar%2C%20who%20himself%20met%20Union%20ministers%20regarding%20possible%20resolution%20of%20farmers%E2%80%99%20issues%2C%20said%20demands%20raised%20by%20farmers%20are%20of%20very%20serious%20nature%20and%20both%20sides%20must%20resolve%20it%20through%20dialogue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20he%20criticised%20the%20AAP%20government%20in%20Punjab%2C%20asserting%20that%20talks%20between%20the%20Union%20government%20and%20the%20farmers%20faced%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20completed%20due%20to%20the%20Punjab%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99%20Bhagwant%20Mann%E2%80%99s%20attempts%20to%20thwart%20the%20discussions%20for%20political%20gains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EMann%2C%20it%20is%20learnt%2C%20had%20attended%20all%20meetings%20held%20between%20the%20Union%20government%20and%20farmer%20leaders%20in%20Chandigarh%20over%20the%20past%20two%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EBesides%20Jakhar%2C%20another%20state%20BJP%20leader%20and%20former%20Punjab%20chief%20minister%2C%20Captain%20Amarinder%20Singh%2C%20criticised%20the%20excessive%20use%20of%20force%20by%20the%20Haryana%20police%20in%20dealing%20with%20farmers%20and%20even%20urged%20chief%20minister%20Manohar%20Lal%20Khattar%20to%20take%20strict%20action%20against%20the%20guilty%20policemen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3ESingh%20also%20met%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20last%20week%20and%20said%20that%20he%20had%20a%20detailed%20discussion%20with%20him%20while%20expressing%20confidence%20that%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20issues%20will%20be%20resolved%20very%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708867012000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F27210340%2FEffect.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-in-tight-spot-over-fresh-round-of-farmers-protest-reconciliation-with-akali-dal-on-back-burner%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20per%20poll%20observers%2C%20the%20biggest%20setback%20for%20BJP%20is%20the%20pause%20on%20talks%20for%20a%20potential%20alliance%20with%20the%20Shiromani%20Akali%20Dal.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A13%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-in-tight-spot-over-fresh-round-of-farmers-protest-reconciliation-with-akali-dal-on-back-burner%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Israel%20mulls%20ceasefire%20plan%20as%20progress%20reported%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708866374000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F11579%2Fproduction%2F_132733017_gettyimages-2028789111.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-68396335%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20comes%20as%20police%20break%20up%20protests%20in%20Tel%20Aviv%20calling%20for%20the%20prime%20minister's%20resignation.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A943%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-68396335%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-68396335.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-68396335.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Invisible%20Farmers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F01%2F26105211%2FWhatsApp-Image-2021-01-26-at-10.46.34-AM.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20a%20difficult%20truth%20to%20accept%20that%20the%20images%20of%20dishevelled%20but%20spirited%20farmers%20being%20shown%20in%20endless%20loops%20on%20our%20TV%20are%20somewhat%20lopsided.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELook%20closely.%20The%20images%20%E2%80%93%20mostly%20of%20males%20of%20all%20ages%20marching%20with%20weather-beaten%20faces%2C%20talking%20to%20the%20media%2C%20driving%20tractors%20or%20carts%20and%20scattered%20in%20little%20groups%20trying%20to%20break%20police%20cordons%20%E2%80%93%20represent%20the%20face%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20farming%20crisis%20only%20partially.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20key%20indicators%20of%20the%20cycle%20of%20distress%20and%20endless%20exploitation%20are%20actually%20hordes%20of%20invisible%20women%20farmers%2C%20seldom%20recognised%20as%20equal%20to%20male%20farmers%20either%20within%20homes%20or%20out%20in%20the%20fields%2C%20as%20well%20as%20in%20formal%20meetings%20between%20farmers%E2%80%99%20bodies%20and%20representatives%20of%20the%20government.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20246px)%2085vw%2C%20246px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F05103945%2FIMG_1783-246x300.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mrinal%20Pande%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22246%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F05103945%2FIMG_1783-246x300.jpg%20246w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F05103945%2FIMG_1783.jpg%20525w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-642789%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22300%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEach%20time%20crucial%20issues%20pertaining%20to%20their%20livelihood%20are%20being%20discussed%2C%20the%20women%20farmers%20are%20omitted.%20Why%3F%20Because%20it%20is%20accepted%20widely%20that%20their%20problems%20as%20cultivators%20can%20be%20no%20different%20from%20those%20brought%20to%20the%20table%20by%20their%20males.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20the%20problems%20female%20cultivators%20(both%20small%20landholders%20or%20labourers)%20face%20are%20not%20triggered%20by%20just%20passing%20El%20Ni%C3%B1o%20years%2C%20floods%20or%20droughts.%20We%20have%20to%20realise%20how%20they%20are%20structural%20and%20embedded%20in%20our%20farming%20communities%E2%80%99%20genderised%20norms%20and%20attitudes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20per%20Census%20norms%2C%20a%20cultivator%20is%20a%20person%20%E2%80%9Cengaged%20in%20cultivation%20of%20land%20owned%20or%20held%20from%20government%20or%20held%20from%20private%20persons%20or%20institutions%20in%20payment%20for%20money%2C%20kind%20or%20share.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMost%20women%20farmers%20do%20not%20qualify%20formally%20as%20land%20owners.%20What%20land%20they%20have%20is%20in%20the%20name%20of%20their%20males%2C%20and%20many%20who%20are%20widowed%20or%20abandoned%20by%20their%20men%20are%20forced%20to%20sell%20their%20holdings%20and%20become%20landless%20agricultural%20labourers%20working%20in%20others%E2%80%99%20fields.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20no%20secret%20that%20land%20is%20scarce.%20The%20share%20of%20cultivators%20in%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20total%20agricultural%20workers%20reduced%20substantially%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fprsindia.org%2Fbudgets%2Fparliament%2Fdemand-for-grants-analysis-agriculture-and-farmers-welfare%5C%22%3E(72%25%20to%2045%25)%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20fifties%20till%202011%20and%20the%20proportion%20of%20farm%20labourers%20in%20the%20same%20period%20shot%20up%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fprsindia.org%2Fbudgets%2Fparliament%2Fdemand-for-grants-analysis-agriculture-and-farmers-welfare%5C%22%3E28%25%20to%2055%25%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECultivation%20is%20the%20largest%20employer%20of%20women%20in%20rural%20areas.%20Put%20these%20together%20and%20calculate%20how%20much%20the%20current%20debate%20on%20farmers%E2%80%99%20distress%20is%20leaving%20out.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOur%20official%20myopia%20is%20also%20mirrored%20on%20our%20TV%20screens.%20As%20the%20cameras%20pan%20the%20crowd%2C%20you%20see%20women%20mostly%20as%20part%20of%20a%20mass%20raising%20slogans%20and%20waving%20fists%20in%20the%20daytime.%20Most%20have%20their%20heads%20covered%20and%20when%20they%20talk%20to%20the%20media%2C%20the%20older%20women%20take%20the%20mic.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%20(spent%20dodging%20shells%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Elathi%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Es%20like%20their%20men)%2C%20all%20of%20them%20turn%20into%20faceless%20cooks%20rolling%20out%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Echapati%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Es%20and%20ladling%20out%20curries%20for%20the%20hungry%20marchers.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMessy%2C%20complex%2C%20miserable%20and%20happy%20by%20turns%2C%20from%20Kerala%20to%20Uttarakhand%2C%20the%20lives%20of%20farmers%E2%80%99%20wives%20are%20the%20real%20miracle%20sustaining%20the%20community.%20These%20women%20are%20not%20listed%20as%20the%20primary%20owners%20of%20the%20fields%20they%20cultivate%20and%20have%20no%20access%20to%20government%20subsidies%2C%20unlike%20males%20(even%20those%20who%20remain%20city-based%20gentleman%20farmers%20leasing%20their%20lands%20each%20year).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwomen%2Ffarmers-protest-once-again-brought-to-fore-the-power-of-women-in-mass-mobilisations%5C%22%3EFarmers%E2%80%99%20Protest%20Once%20Again%20Brought%20to%20Fore%20the%20Power%20of%20Women%20in%20Mass%20Mobilisations%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWatching%20the%20animated%20discussions%20in%20manels%20among%20agricultural%20scientists%2C%20agricultural%20reporters%2C%20government%20officials%20and%20retired%20heads%20of%20agricultural%20institutes%20and%20colleges%2C%20it%20is%20distressing%20to%20see%20that%20(only%20occasionally)%20the%20anchor%20is%20the%20only%20female%20present.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%20has%20produced%20some%20fine%20women%20agricultural%20scientists%20and%20economists%20%E2%80%93%20from%20Bina%20Agarwal%2C%20Rajshree%20Agarwal%2C%20Vandana%20Shiva%20and%20Inderjit%20Kaur%20Borthakur%2C%20to%20name%20a%20few%20%E2%80%93%20but%20they%20are%20glaringly%20absent%20from%20expert%20panels%20and%20farmers%E2%80%99%20representative%20committees.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20the%20particular%20caste%2Fgender%20and%20land%20ownership-related%20problems%20female%20farmers%20face%20remain%20largely%20unarticulated%20and%20undiscussed.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20total%20disregard%20for%20a%20whole%20group%20qua%20group%20is%20the%20most%20debased%2C%20irrational%20and%20undemocratic%20of%20omissions%20during%20a%20crisis%20of%20the%20size%20our%20farming%20community%20is%20facing.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESometimes%20%E2%80%93%20only%20sometimes%20%E2%80%93%20someone%20like%20Khashthi%20Devi%20Koranga%20says%20%E2%80%98to%20hell%20with%20it%E2%80%99%20one%20day%20and%20takes%20the%20first%20step%20on%20her%20own.%20How%20many%20of%20us%20have%20heard%20of%20her%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKhashthi%20Devi%20is%20of%20a%20far-flung%20area%20named%20Kapkot%20in%20Uttarakhand%E2%80%99s%20Bageshwar%20district.%20She%20travelled%20a%20few%20months%20ago%20all%20the%20way%20to%20Hyderabad%20in%20Telangana%20to%20receive%20the%20%E2%80%98best%20farmer%E2%80%99%20award%20at%20the%20International%20Conference%20on%20System%20of%20Crop%20Intensification%20for%20Climate-Smart%20Livelihood%20and%20Nutritional%20Security.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKhashthi%20Devi%20is%20a%20master%20trainer%20who%20has%20trained%20and%20organised%202%2C500%20women%20from%2015%20villages%20in%20her%20area%20and%20helped%20small-holding%20female%20farmers%20like%20herself%20in%20forming%20self-help%20groups.%20These%20women%20now%20help%20each%20other%20produce%20as%20much%20as%20they%20can%20from%20their%20small%20and%20often%20unirrigated%20land%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fagriculture.uk.gov.in%2F%5C%22%3Eonly%2045%25%20of%20land%20in%20the%20state%20is%20irrigated%3C%2Fa%3E).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22The%20Hills%20Are%20Unforgiving%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fthe-hills-are-unforgiving%5C%22%3EThe%20Hills%20Are%20Unforgiving%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUttarakhand%20is%20by%20no%20means%20a%20rich%20agrarian%20state%20given%20the%20difficult%20terrain%20and%20its%20mercurial%20weather%20patterns%20having%20become%20even%20more%20unpredictable%20of%20late.%20The%20state%E2%80%99s%20women%20farmers%20all%20also%20tackle%20major%20unseen%2C%20seldom%20spoken%20of%20problems%20that%20affect%20farming%20women%20everywhere%3A%20problems%20of%20caste%2C%20gender%20and%20climate%20change.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAny%20woman%20tackling%20these%20runs%20into%20them%20as%20soon%20as%20she%20starts%20to%20cast%20off%20the%20age-old%20ostracisation%20of%20her%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ehaq%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(rights).%20Change%20began%20in%202017%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gaonconnection.com%2Flead-stories%2Futtarakhand-khastidevi-farmer-women-fpo-sustainable-agriculture-international-award-crop-intensification-technique-51578%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EKhashthi%20Devi%20told%20a%20reporter%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%20remember%20going%20from%20house%20to%20house%20convincing%20people%20to%20try%20line%20sowing%20methods%20for%20a%20better%20yield.%20Older%20men%20in%20the%20village%20mocked%20me%20and%20discouraged%20women%20from%20departing%20from%20traditional%20farming%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20there%20are%20deeper%20problems%20facing%20the%20hill%20farmers%E2%80%99%20community%2C%20tearing%20families%20apart%20and%20leaving%20only%20an%20ageing%20population%20to%20care%20for%20derelict%20villages%20where%20wild%20animals%20come%20foraging%20more%20and%20more%20frequently%20with%20the%20cutting%20down%20of%20forests.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EPahad%20ka%20paani%20aur%20pahaad%20ki%20jawani%20yahan%20ke%20logon%20ke%20kaam%20nahin%20aati%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(our%20waters%20and%20our%20youth%20no%20longer%20serve%20the%20local%20needs)%2C%20I%20have%20heard%20countless%20times.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYoung%20males%20who%20can%20find%20other%20jobs%20have%20copped%20out%20as%20men%20do%20and%20chosen%20to%20work%20in%20the%20plains.%20Since%20the%20land%20is%20mostly%20registered%20in%20their%20names%2C%20schemes%20like%20the%20PM%20Crop%20Insurance%20scheme%20are%20of%20no%20use%20for%20female%20farmers%20to%20collect%20compensation%20for%20lost%20crops.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CEarlier%2C%20men%20went%20alone%3B%20now%2C%20they%20take%20their%20young%20wives%20and%20children%20along.%20Young%20girls%20marry%20these%20days%20only%20on%20the%20condition%20that%20they%20will%20not%20do%20%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Egobar%20paani%20ka%20kaam%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%99%20%5Bcattle%20care%20and%20fetching%20water%20from%20far-off%20rivers%20or%20springs%5D%2C%E2%80%9D%20an%20old%20mother%20tells%20me%20as%20she%20bangs%20on%20a%20cluster%20of%20empty%20cans%20to%20chase%20away%20monkeys%20robbing%20her%20orchards.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20can%20one%20do%3F%20Even%20if%20daughters-in-law%20stay%20back%20for%20a%20few%20years%2C%20once%20the%20boys%20are%20five%2C%20they%20take%20their%20children%20and%20live%20in%20a%20rented%20room%20in%20the%20city%20in%20the%20name%20of%20educating%20them.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EBaboo%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20how%20can%20we%20the%20grandparents%20say%20no%20to%20that%3F%20It%20is%20the%20question%20of%20the%20boys%E2%80%99%20future%2C%20no%3F%20We%20can%E2%80%99t%20abandon%20our%20ancestors%E2%80%99%20land%2C%20but%20they%20have%20no%20interest%20in%20village%20life%20after%20getting%20a%20degree.%20They%20want%20to%20work%20in%20hotels%20as%20tourist%20guides%20%5Band%5D%20taxi%20operators.%20Who%20wants%20to%20stay%20and%20fetch%20the%20water%20and%20feed%20the%20cattle%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F25172650%2F7152944903_85a514fcea_c.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F25172650%2F7152944903_85a514fcea_c.jpg%20800w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F25172650%2F7152944903_85a514fcea_c-300x200.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-698816%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22536%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESince%20land%20is%20mostly%20registered%20in%20male%20farmers%E2%80%99%20names%2C%20schemes%20like%20the%20PM%20Crop%20Insurance%20scheme%20are%20of%20no%20use%20for%20female%20farmers%20to%20collect%20compensation%20for%20lost%20crops.%20Photo%3A%20Allan%20Hopkins%2FFlickr.%20CC%20BY-NC-ND%202.0.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20new%20migrations%20are%20increasingly%20leaving%20aged%20women%20and%20a%20few%20old%20men%20behind%20as%20caretakers%20of%20family%20houses%20and%20orchards.%20Most%20are%20too%20old%20for%20the%20hard%20hands-on%20work%20the%20land%20demands.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWorking%20as%20labourers%20is%20also%20not%20an%20option%20for%20them.%20Payment%20for%20planting%2C%20winnowing%20and%20pounding%20is%20anyhow%20only%20partially%20in%20cash%20and%20mostly%20in%20kind%2C%20for%20example%20with%20grains%20and%20hay%20for%20the%20cattle.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOf%20this%20rural%20population%20of%20landless%20females%2C%20the%20Dalit%20women%20suffer%20the%20most.%20Dalits%20are%20mostly%20landless%20and%20many%20of%20them%20do%20not%20have%20cattle%20to%20make%20manure%20out%20of%20cow%20dung.%20Apart%20from%20facing%20frequent%20pest%20attacks%20and%20droughts%2C%20Dalits%20mostly%20live%20on%20the%20peripheries%20of%20villages%2C%20where%20they%20are%20increasingly%20vulnerable%20to%20wild%20animal%20attacks.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20village%20is%20inhabited%20only%20until%20the%20two%20of%20us%20are%20alive%2C%E2%80%9D%20two%20elderly%20women%20sitting%20listlessly%20outside%20their%20derelict%20home%20in%20a%20village%20in%20Paudi%20Gadhwal%2C%20told%20a%20reporter%20from%20the%20Hindi%20edition%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EDown%20to%20Earth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Uttarakhand%20is%20full%20of%20such%20ghost%20villages%2C%20Raju%20Sajwan%2C%20the%20frequent%20traveller%20to%20these%20areas%2C%20has%20been%20reporting.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20clear%20that%20leaving%20women%20farmers%20and%20their%20spokespersons%20out%20of%20national%20debates%20and%20decision-making%20means%20leaving%20out%20a%20vast%20area%20of%20culture%20and%20gender-specific%20problems.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20an%20eyewitness%2C%20one%20can%20only%20say%20that%20what%20the%20ageing%20generation%20of%20landless%20Uttarakhand%20women%20are%20saying%20at%20the%20end%20of%20their%20hard%20lives%20is%20an%20awful%20truth%20we%20have%20long%20been%20in%20denial%20about.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3ESaakhi%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0is%20a%20Sunday%20column%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fmrinal-pande%5C%22%3EMrinal%20Pande%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%20which%20she%20writes%20of%20what%20she%20sees%20and%20also%20participates%20in.%20That%20has%20been%20her%20burden%20to%20bear%20ever%20since%20she%20embarked%20on%20a%20life%20as%20a%20journalist%2C%20writer%2C%20editor%2C%20author%20and%20as%20chairperson%20of%20Prasar%20Bharti.%20Her%20journey%20of%20being%20a%20witness-participant%20continues.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708866003000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F01%2F26105211%2FWhatsApp-Image-2021-01-26-at-10.46.34-AM.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwomen%2Fthe-invisible-farmers-saakhi%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20lives%20of%20farmers%E2%80%99%20wives%20are%20the%20real%20miracle%20sustaining%20the%20community.%20Unlike%20their%20male%20counterparts%2C%20these%20women%20are%20not%20listed%20as%20the%20primary%20owners%20of%20the%20fields%20they%20cultivate%20and%20have%20no%20access%20to%20government%20subsidies.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwomen%2Fthe-invisible-farmers-saakhi%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%20Has%20Allowed%20its%20Authority%20to%20Be%20Diluted%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25222448%2FSupreme-Court-1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EFormer%20Delhi%20high%20court%20judge%20Justice%20Rekha%20Sharma%20delivered%20the%20following%20remarks%20at%20a%20seminar%20organised%20by%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3Ethe%20Campaign%20for%20Judicial%20Accountability%20and%20Reforms%2C%20in%20collaboration%20with%20%3C%2Fem%3EThe%20Wire%20%3Cem%3Eand%20%3C%2Fem%3ELiveLaw%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20am%20thankful%20to%20the%20organisers%20for%20having%20provided%20me%20with%20this%20opportunity%20to%20be%20with%20you%20all%20today.%20Though%20I%20am%20almost%20a%20stranger%20to%20the%20actual%20working%20of%20the%20Roster%20system%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20let%20me%20share%20my%20own%20little%20experience%20of%20what%20I%20have%20heard%20and%20observed.%20The%20subject%20has%20taken%20me%20back%20to%20the%20year%20I%20enrolled%20myself%20as%20an%20Advocate.%20That%20was%20the%20day%20my%20family%20looked%20at%20me%20with%20awe%20and%20amazement.%20It%20was%20because%20none%20of%20them%20except%20my%20father%20had%20ever%20seen%20a%20court%20room.%20My%20resolve%20to%20practice%20law%20was%20difficult%20for%20them%20to%20digest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKnowing%20none%2C%20and%20with%20no%20brief%2C%20I%20would%20sit%20in%20some%20court%20room%20or%20the%20other%2C%20listen%20to%20the%20arguing%20counsel%20and%20comeback%20home%20briefless%20and%20with%20empty%20pocket.%20But%2C%20then%2C%20miracles%20do%20happen.%20It%20was%20a%20Friday.%20I%20saw%20an%20elderly%20lady%20lawyer%20getting%20up%2C%20bowing%20her%20head%2C%20and%20saying%20something.%20Two%20serious%20looking%20judges%20raised%20their%20heads%2C%20looked%20at%20her%2C%20%E2%80%9CDismissed%E2%80%9D%2C%20said%20their%20Lordships.%20The%20lady%20lawyer%20passed%20by%20my%20seat%2C%20red%20faced%2C%20head%20jerking%2C%20murmuring%20something%20inaudible.%20While%20she%20lost%20her%20brief%2C%20it%20made%20my%20day.%20It%20carved%20my%20future.%20I%20followed%20her%20to%20her%20chamber%2C%20introduced%20myself%2C%20told%20her%20I%20was%20watching%20her%20great%20performance%2C%20and%20that%20I%20wanted%20to%20be%20her%20junior.%20She%20looked%20at%20me%2C%20asked%20me%20to%20have%20a%20seat%2C%20and%20agreed%20to%20take%20me%20as%20her%20junior.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20long%20time%2C%20I%20would%20carry%20her%20bulky%20files%2C%20follow%20her%20from%20one%20court%20room%20to%20another%2C%20and%20became%20immune%20to%20the%20epithets%2C%20good%20or%20bad%20for%20the%20different%20Benches.%20However%2C%20one%20thing%20is%20clear%20to%20me.What%20was%20earlier%20being%20said%20in%20whispering%20tones%2C%20in%20present%20times%20is%20being%20talked%20openly.%20And%2C%20it%20is%20something%20called%20%E2%80%9CBench%20fixing%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20with%20the%20passage%20of%20time%20I%20became%20a%20busy%20lawyer%2C%20the%20Bench%20and%20its%20allure%20became%20overwhelming.%20I%20was%20selected%20for%20the%20Higher%20Judicial%20Service%2C%20and%20a%20few%20years%20later%20elevated%20to%20the%20Bench.%20However%2C%20somewhere%20in%20the%20back%20of%20my%20mind%2C%20the%20epithet%20%E2%80%9CBench%20fixing%E2%80%9D%20kept%20haunting.%20And%2C%20to%20my%20surprise%20and%20dismay%2C%20I%20realized%20that%20though%20in%20the%20High%20Court%2C%20the%20Registry%E2%80%99s%20hands%20were%20clipped%20by%20the%20Roster%20System%2C%20that%20system%20too%20was%20not%20free%20from%20rat%E2%80%99s%20smell.%20And%20that%20smell%20emanated%20principally%20from%20the%20pen%20of%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20who%20was%20incharge%20of%20the%20Roster.%20None%20of%20the%20so-called%20Service%20Judges%20was%20ever%20assigned%20important%20constitutional%20matters%2C%20habeas%20corpus%20or%20other%20writ%20petitions%20involving%20important%20questions%20of%20law.%20All%20such%20cases%20went%20to%20judges%20directly%20elevated%20from%20the%20Bar.%20As%20if%2C%20the%20judges%20from%20the%20Bar%20were%20paragon%20of%20knowledge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Narasimha%20Rao%E2%80%99s%20bribery%20case%20which%20revolved%20around%20the%20interpretation%20of%20Article%20105%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20and%20involving%20not%20only%20the%20person%20who%20held%20the%20position%20of%20the%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20but%20other%20equally%20important%20persons%2C%20showed%20not%20only%20the%20judge%E2%80%99s%20indefatigable%20courage%2C%20but%20also%20his%20complete%20grasp%20over%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India%2C%20and%20its%20interpretation.%20But%2C%20what%20is%20important%20in%20the%20present%20context%20is%20that%20the%20author%20of%20the%20judgement%20was%20a%20service%20judge.%20Make%20no%20mistake%2C%20the%20case%20was%20not%20assigned%20to%20him.%20It%20landed%20before%20him%20because%20he%20happened%20to%20be%20sitting%20in%20a%20criminal%20roster%2C%20and%20the%20question%20with%20regard%20to%20the%20interpretation%20of%20Article%20105%20of%20the%20Constitution%20arose%20out%20of%20that%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%2C%20what%20is%20the%20present%20state%20of%20affairs%2C%20particularly%20in%20Supreme%20Court.%20It%20has%20taken%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20more%20than%20five%20years%20to%20decide%20Electrol%20Bond%20petitions%20involving%20the%20very%20existence%2C%20and%20fairness%20of%20the%20electrol%20process.%20Chief%20Justices%20came%20and%20Chief%20Justices%20went%20away%2C%20each%20shying%20away%20from%20taking%20up%20the%20issue%20head%20on.%20To%20be%20fair%20to%20the%20then%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%2C%20even%20in%20the%20height%20of%20emergency%2C%20when%20Smt.%20Indra%20Gandhi%20reigned%20Supreme%2C%20he%20did%20not%20shy%20away%20from%20constituting%20a%20Bench%20and%20taking%20up%20the%20matter%20of%20%3Cem%3EADM%20Jabalpur%3C%2Fem%3E.%20It%20is%20a%20different%20matter%20that%20its%20outcome%20was%20highly%20damning%20to%20the%20fundamental%20rights%20of%20the%20citizen%2C%20and%20it%20remains%20an%20ugly%20spot%20on%20the%20fair%20face%20of%20the%20judiciary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhy%20no%20urgency%20was%20felt%20or%20realised%20by%20one%20Chief%20Justice%20after%20another%20in%20the%20Electoral%20Bonds%20cases%20or%20others%20similar%20matters%20involving%20the%20rights%20of%20the%20citizens%3F%20In%20the%20interregnum%2C%20much%20water%20has%20already%20flown%20under%20the%20bridge.%20One%20general%20election%2C%20and%20many%20elections%20to%20the%20State%20Legislatures%2C%20had%20taken%20place%20in%20the%20meanwhile.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%2C%20imagine%2C%20when%20a%20judgement%20like%20in%20the%20Electoral%20Bonds%20matter%20comes%20protecting%20the%20rights%20of%20the%20citizens%2C%20they%20are%20not%20only%20pleasantly%20surprised%2C%20but%20feel%20so%20relieved%20as%20to%20hail%20and%20thank%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20even%20when%20it%20has%20only%20performed%20its%20constitutional%20duty.%20And%20when%20it%20does%20that%2C%20it%20neither%20needs%20applause%20nor%20brickbats.%20But%20the%20fact%20that%20such%20was%20the%20reaction%20shows%20how%20much%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20lost%20in%20terms%20of%20credibility%20in%20the%20field%20of%20justice%20delivery%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20is%20no%20longer%20taken%20as%20the%20last%20word%20on%20any%20such%20pronouncement.%20It%20is%20already%20being%20said%20that%20the%20government%20may%20move%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20for%20review%2C%20or%20the%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%20and%20the%20Election%20Commission%20may%20ask%20for%20further%20time%20to%20carry%20out%20its%20directions%2C%20or%20the%20government%20may%20even%20bring%20an%20Ordinance%20to%20nullify%20the%20effect%20of%20the%20judgement.%20After%20all%2C%20the%20government%20did%20bring%20an%20Ordinance%20to%20reverse%20the%20judgement%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20the%20matter%20of%20selection%20of%20the%20Election%20Commissioners%20by%20removing%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20as%20being%20part%20of%20such%20selection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhy%20have%20things%20come%20to%20such%20a%20pass%3F%20The%20government%20is%20not%20entirely%20to%20be%20blamed.%20Somewhere%20down%20the%20line%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20allowed%20its%20authority%20to%20dilute.%20Though%20it%20is%20unfortunate%2C%20keeping%20in%20view%20the%20past%20performance%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20one%20feels%2C%20it%20is%20the%20government%20which%20will%20have%20the%20last%20laugh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELet%20me%20take%20you%20to%20the%20past.%20The%20aggrieved%20citizen%20was%20known%20by%20the%20name%20of%20Maneka%20Gandhi.%20Our%20Supreme%20Court%20said%2C%20and%20I%20quote%2C%20that%20%E2%80%9Cspeedy%20trial%20is%20a%20dynamic%20and%20progressive%20program%20of%20legal%20assistance%2C%20an%20essential%20ingredient%20of%20the%20right%20to%20life%20and%20liberty%20and%20flows%20directly%20from%20Article%2021%20of%20the%20Constitution%E2%80%9D.%20Brave%20words%2C%20but%20lost%20somewhere%20in%20the%20wilderness%20of%20the%20Roster%20regime.%20You%20do%20not%20live%20on%20words%20alone.%20They%20need%20a%20heart.%20And%20a%20heart%20that%20flutters.%20Thousands%20and%20thousands%20are%20rotting%20in%20jails%2C%20standing%20in%20the%20corridors%20of%20courts%20of%20justice%2C%20day%20in%20and%20day%20out%2C%20with%20prayers%20on%20their%20lips%2C%20hoping%20for%20the%20rule%2C%20%E2%80%9CBail%20not%20Jail%E2%80%9Dto%20resurrect.%20But%20it%20surfaces%20only%20for%20the%20chosen%20few.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESiddique%20Kappan%2C%20a%20journalist%20who%20was%20arrested%20on%20October%205%2C%202020%2C%20got%20bail%20after%20more%20than%20two%20years.%20When%20he%20approached%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20under%20Article%2032%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20the%20then%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20remarked%20that%20we%20want%20to%20discourage%20Article%2032%20petitions%2C%20and%20he%20was%20sent%20back%20to%20the%20High%20Court.%20More%20recently%2C%20Supreme%20Court%20declined%20to%20hear%20an%20Article%2032%20petition%20involving%20the%20arrest%20of%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20a%20State%20who%20alleged%20that%20he%20was%20arrested%20on%20no%20evidence%2C%20and%20with%20the%20sole%20aim%20of%20destabilising%20his%20duly%20elected%20government.%20The%20Bench%20observed%2C%20%E2%80%9Cwhy%20have%20you%20come%20here%20directly%E2%80%9D.%20This%20observation%20was%20made%20notwithstanding%20the%20fact%20that%20many%20a%20times%20in%20the%20past%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20been%20entertaining%20Article%2032%20petitions%20depending%20upon%20the%20urgency%20and%20gravity%20of%20the%20matter.%20And%2C%20more%20importantly%2C%20the%20observation%20has%20come%20notwithstanding%20the%20golden%20words%20of%20B.R.%20Ambedkar%2C%20the%20architect%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20describing%20Article%2032%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9Cheart%20and%20soul%20of%20the%20Constitution%E2%80%9D.%20Is%20Article%2032%20to%20be%20treated%20as%20a%20dead%20letter%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERemember%20the%20landmark%20judgement%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findiankanoon.org%2Fdoc%2F1373215%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EHussanara%20Khatoon%20vs.%20State%20of%20Bihar%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3F%20Recollect%20what%20the%20judges%20said%3F%20Let%20me%20remind%20you.%20They%20not%20only%20felt%20that%20there%20was%20a%20shocking%20state%20of%20affairs%20so%20far%20as%20the%20administration%20of%20law%20and%20order%20is%20concerned%2C%20but%20also%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20legal%20system%20has%20lost%20its%20credibility%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArun%20Shourie%20has%20beautifully%20described%20the%20present%20state%20of%20judiciary%20in%20his%20remarkably%20readable%20book%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Commission%20for%20Lost%20Causes%3C%2Fem%3E.%20He%20calls%20the%20judges%20as%20%E2%80%9CLions%20under%20the%20throne%E2%80%9D.%20The%20misfortune%20is%20that%20many%20of%20them%20have%20not%20only%20lost%20their%20teeth%20but%20roar%20too%2C%20leaving%20the%20ordinary%20citizen%20to%20the%20mercy%20of%20predators%20and%20jackals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20we%20find%20today%20is%20that%20while%20a%20powerful%20person%20gets%20bail%20on%20an%20experimental%20basis%2C%20men%20like%20Umar%20Khalid%20are%20withering%20away%2C%20unwept%2C%20unsung%20and%20unheard%2C%20and%20so%20fed%20up%20that%20coming%20out%20of%20the%20corridors%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20is%20itself%20considered%20a%20relief.%20While%20a%20journalist%20spends%20time%20in%20jail%20for%20the%20mere%20crime%20of%20performing%20his%20duty%2C%20an%20old%20and%20ailing%20man%20unable%20to%20even%20sip%20water%20is%20denied%20basic%20medical%20aid%2C%20and%20is%20made%20to%20suffer%20and%20die%20behind%20the%20bars.%20What%20has%20happened%20to%20Article%2021%3F%20Why%20have%20those%20swearing%20by%20the%20Constitution%20forgotten%20cases%20like%20Hussainara%2C%20M.H.%20Hoskot%2C%20Sunil%20Batra%20and%20A.K.%20Roy%3F%20What%20has%20happened%20to%20those%20brave%20words%20in%3Cem%3E%20Rattan%20Singh%20versus%20State%20of%20Punja%3C%2Fem%3Eb%20(AIR%201982%20Supreme%20Court%201)%2C%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6If%20freedom%20and%20liberty%20are%20to%20have%20any%20meaning%20in%20our%20democratic%20setup%2C%20it%20is%20essential%20that%20at%20least%20those%20safeguards%20are%20not%20denied.%E2%80%9D%20Is%20our%20judiciary%20pushing%20down%20who%20deserve%20to%20be%20pushed%20down%20and%20pulling%20up%20who%20deserve%20to%20be%20pulled%20up%2C%20or%20is%20it%20just%20becoming%20gilded%20tomb%20of%20a%20failed%20talent%3F%20The%20question%20is%20not%20who%20is%20making%20them%20dance.%20The%20question%20is%20who%20is%20dancing%20and%20why%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20I%20was%20penning%20these%20lines%2C%20I%20had%20before%20me%20two%20headlines%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Without%20a%20comment%2C%20I%20am%20reading%20them%20out%20to%20you%2C%20leaving%20it%20to%20you%20to%20react.%20Here%20is%20the%20first%20one.%20A%20Bench%20of%20Justice%20B.R.%20Gavai%20and%20Sandeep%20Mehta%20observed%20%E2%80%9Cwhen%20the%20question%20of%20liberty%20of%20a%20person%20is%20involved%2C%20even%20a%C2%A0day%E2%80%99s%20delay%20counts%E2%80%9D%20(January%2018%2C%202024)%20and%20here%20is%20the%20second%20one%2C%20%E2%80%9C24%20years%20after%20a%20man%20dies%20in%20police%20custody%2C%20ex-cop%20sentenced%20to%2010%20years%20jail%E2%80%9D.%20How%20do%20you%20reconcile%20the%20two%3F%20One%20decries%20even%20a%20day%E2%80%99s%20delay%20and%20the%20other%20tells%20us%20of%20delay%20of%2024%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERemember%20those%20five%20judges%20of%20the%20press%20conference%20fame.%20One%20of%20them%2C%20a%20friend%20from%20days%20of%20our%20mutual%20struggle%20at%20the%20Bar%2C%20is%20present%20today.%20What%20happened%20thereafter%3F%20Any%20reform%3F%20Any%20improvement%3F%20Let%20us%20remember%20that%20a%20driver%E2%80%99s%20competence%20is%20not%20established%20by%20his%20dress%20or%20his%20religious%20fervor%20made%20public%2C%20but%20by%20making%20his%20passengers%20reach%20their%20destination%20safely.%20A%20judge%20must%20fall%20in%20love%20with%20the%20Constitution%20before%20he%20approaches%20it.%20The%20original%20is%20beautiful.%20Its%20reach%20is%20not%20limited.%20It%20is%20not%20the%20Roster%2C%20it%20is%20the%20judge%20who%20assigns%20the%20cases%2C%20and%20it%20is%20the%20judge%20who%20decides%20the%20matter.%3Cbr%3E%5CnShakespeare%20in%20Julius%20Caesar%20writes%3A%20%E2%80%9CHis%20life%20was%20gentle%2C%20and%20the%20elements%20so%20mixed%20in%20him%20that%20Nature%20might%20stand-up.%20And%20say%20to%20all%20the%20world.%20This%20was%20a%20man.%E2%80%9D%20Are%20we%20today%20too%20sure%20of%20the%20presence%20of%20such%20a%20man%3F%20If%20not%2C%20surely%2C%20we%20need%20him%2C%20though%20many%20today%20are%20seen%20taking%20a%20deep%20breath%20and%20agreeing%20with%20Meer%20Taqi%20Meer%3A%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EIbtadaai%20ishq%20hai%2C%20rota%20hai%20kya%20agey%20agey%20dekhiye%20hota%20hai%20kya.%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20having%20said%20all%20this%2C%20I%20will%20be%20unfair%20to%20the%20Roster%20System%2C%20and%20to%20its%20Master%2C%20by%20not%20pointing%20out%20at%20least%20three%20pronounced%20advantages%20of%20the%20Roster%20System%20and%20which%2C%20fortunately%20or%20unfortunately%2C%20have%20already%20become%20public%20and%2C%20they%20are%20as%20follows%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E1.%20The%20Master%20of%20Roster%20can%20constitute%20a%20Bench%20of%20his%20own%20choice%20and%20himself%20preside%20over%20it%20even%20in%20a%20very%20personal%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2.%20By%20intelligently%20making%20use%20of%20that%20power%2C%20he%20can%20assure%20himself%2C%20even%20after%20his%20retirement%2C%20a%20cozy%20job%20like%20a%20seat%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20or%20Governorship%20in%20some%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E3.%20By%20intelligently%20using%20that%20power%2C%20he%20can%20equally%20benefit%20his%20very%20worthy%20and%20dearest%20colleagues%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThank%20you%20very%20much.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708863927000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25222448%2FSupreme-Court-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fthe-supreme-court-has-allowed-its-authority-to-be-diluted%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22At%20a%20seminar%20organised%20by%20the%20Campaign%20for%20Judicial%20Accountability%20and%20Reforms%2C%20in%20collaboration%20with%20The%20Wire%20and%20LiveLaw%2C%20Justice%20Rekha%20Sharma%20discussed%20why%20the%20present%20state%20of%20affairs%20in%20the%20court%20needs%20remedy.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fthe-supreme-court-has-allowed-its-authority-to-be-diluted%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22RLD-BJP%20Alliance%3A%20What%20Does%20the%20Changed%20Political%20Equations%20Now%20Hold%20for%20Western%20Uttar%20Pradesh%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F23172343%2FScreen-Shot-2024-02-23-at-5.22.55-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMuzaffarnagar%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%20motorcycle%20rally%20led%20by%20the%20BJP%20passes%20through%20sugarcane%20fields%20in%20Budhana%2C%20Muzaffarnagar.%20The%20bikes%20are%20decorated%20with%20flags%20of%20the%20saffron%20party%20while%20a%20song%20plays%20in%20the%20background%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98Mazdoor%20kisan%20ke%20haq%20mein%20ye%20alakh%20jagai%20re%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3ERLD%20aayi%20re%2C%20RLD%20aayi%20re%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98(This%20awakening%20is%20happening%20in%20support%20of%20labourers%20and%20farmers%2C%20RLD%20%5BRashtriya%20Lok%20Dal%5D%20has%20come%2C%20RLD%20has%20come).%E2%80%99%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20sugarcane%20plots%20belong%20to%20Shobhan%20Singh%2C%2080%20who%20has%20seen%20the%20influence%20of%20the%20former%20prime%20minister%20Chaudhary%20Charan%20Singh%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20politics.%20A%20%3Cem%3Echaupal%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20been%20set%20up%2C%20at%20the%20edge%20of%20the%20fields%2C%20where%20he%20sits%20with%20a%20hookah.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20his%20thoughts%2C%20Shobhan%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CChaudhary%20Sahib%20deserved%20the%20Bharat%20Ratna%20but%20no%20past%20prime%20minister%20thought%20of%20honouring%20him%20in%20this%20manner.%20Now%20it%20is%20natural%20for%20Chaudhary%20Sahib%E2%80%99s%20grandson%20Jayant%20to%20lean%20towards%20the%20BJP.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20villagers%20nod%20in%20agreement%2C%20puffing%20on%20their%20hookahs%2C%20wondering%20aloud%20farmer%20Shivam%20Choudhary%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EDadda%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20do%20you%20think%20that%20Bharat%20Ratna%20alone%20made%20Jayant%20Choudhary%20distance%20himself%20from%20the%20INDIA%20Alliance%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERLD%E2%80%99s%20prospects%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERLD%20chief%20Jayant%20Chaudhary%20who%20is%20known%20for%20his%20staunch%20opposition%20to%20the%20BJP%20truly%20shocked%20everyone%20by%20parting%20ways%20with%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20(SP)%20and%20switching%20loyalties%20to%20the%20NDA%20within%20hours%20of%20Bharat%20Ratna%20award%20announcement%20for%20Chaudhary%20Charan%20Singh%20on%20February%209.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENext%20day%2C%20while%20speaking%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20a%20turncoat%20Jayant%20said%20aloud%2C%20%E2%80%9CHaving%20been%20in%20the%20opposition%20for%2010%20years%2C%20I%20see%20shades%20of%20Chaudhary%20Charan%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20ideology%20in%20the%20present%20government%E2%80%99s%20working%20style.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20towering%20figure%20in%20farmer%20politics%2C%20Chaudhary%20Charan%20Singh%2C%20had%20devised%20a%20caste%20coalition%20formula%20then%20popularly%20known%20%E2%80%98MAJGAR%E2%80%99%20(Muslim%2C%20Ahir%2C%20Jat%2C%20Gujjar%2C%20and%20Rajput%20communities)%20which%20contributed%20significantly%20to%20his%20success%20in%20the%20western%20part%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ffor-bharat-ratna-chaudhary-charan-singh-politics-meant-the-art-of-possible%5C%22%3EFor%20%E2%80%98Bharat%20Ratna%E2%80%99%20Chaudhary%20Charan%20Singh%2C%20Politics%20Meant%20the%20Art%20of%20the%20Possible%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CChaudhary%20Charan%20Singh%20was%20a%20grassroots%20leader%2C%20representing%20farmers%20of%20all%20castes.%20However%2C%20after%20his%20passing%20away%2C%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20appeal%20diminished%2C%20narrowing%20down%20to%20primarily%20representing%20the%20Jat%20community%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20senior%20journalist%20Brijesh%20Shukla.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20party%E2%80%99s%20downfall%20can%20be%20attributed%20to%20its%20tendency%20to%20align%20with%20larger%20parties%20like%20the%20BJP%20and%20Congress%2C%20rather%20than%20focusing%20on%20strengthening%20its%20own%20foundation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%202014%20elections%2C%20even%20the%20Jat%20support%20base%20of%20the%20RLD%20began%20to%20dwindle%20particularly%20on%20account%20of%20the%20divide%20between%20Muslims%20and%20Jats%20essentially%20following%20the%20infamous%202013%20Muzaffarnagar%20riots%20which%20left%20more%20than%2065%20people%20dead%20and%20thousands%20displaced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20CSDS%20post-poll%20studies%20on%20the%202014%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20the%20BJP%20garnered%2077%25%20of%20the%20Jat%20votes%2C%20a%20stark%20increase%20from%20the%207%25%20it%20received%20in%20the%202012%20Assembly%20elections.%20In%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20there%20was%20a%20considerable%20anticipation%20as%20an%20ambitious%20grand%20alliance%20of%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20(SP)%2C%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20(BSP)%2C%20and%20RLD%20was%20formed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20Muslims%2C%20Jats%20and%20Dalits%20comprising%20approximately%2060%25%20of%20the%20voting%20population%20in%20Western%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20the%20RLD%20harboured%20high%20hopes.%20However%2C%20when%20the%20results%20were%20announced%2C%20it%20sent%20shockwaves%20as%20both%20Ajit%20Singh%20and%20Jayant%20Chaudhary%20lost%20their%20seats%20once%20again%2C%20with%20the%20RLD%20failing%20to%20even%20open%20its%20account%20and%20the%20BJP%20took%20away%2091%25%20of%20the%20Jat%20vote%20share.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%202022%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Assembly%20election%2C%20unfolded%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20massive%20farmer%20protests%20in%20the%20western%20region%20that%20had%20been%20ongoing%20for%20months.%20The%20RLD%20then%20in%20alliance%20with%20the%20SP%20hoped%20to%20bridge%20the%20gap%20between%20Muslims%20and%20Jats.%20However%2C%20the%20results%20remained%20shocking%20for%20RLD%20which%20failed%20to%20win%20more%20than%208%20of%20the%2033%20seats%20it%20contested.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBrijesh%20Shukla%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20the%20RLD%20failed%20to%20secure%20victory%20despite%20being%20part%20of%20the%20grand%20alliance%20in%202019%20or%20amidst%20extensive%20farmer%20protests%20in%202022%2C%20when%20the%20odds%20were%20stacked%20against%20the%20BJP%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20difficult%20to%20see%20how%20they%20could%20emerge%20victorious%20in%202024.%20Jayant%20Chaudhary%20was%20already%20fighting%20a%20losing%20battle.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJayant%20Choudhary%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20join%20the%20NDA%20alliance%20is%20seen%20as%20a%20notable%20advantage%20for%20the%20RLD%2C%20signalling%20the%20possibility%20of%20the%20party%20securing%20a%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20a%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBJP%E2%80%99s%20prospect%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20village%20of%20Firozpur%20Bangar%20in%20Muzaffarnagar%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20Adityanath%20is%20seen%20engaging%20with%20villagers%20during%20a%20%3Cem%3Echaupal%3C%2Fem%3E%20session%2C%20where%20he%20acquaints%20them%20with%20various%20beneficiary%20schemes%20initiated%20by%20the%20central%20and%20state%20governments.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%20launches%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Gram%20Parikrama%20Yatra%20in%20the%20state%2C%20slated%20to%20cover%2050%2C000%20villages%20across%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20Following%20the%20%3Cem%3Echaupal%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20while%20addressing%20villagers%20in%20a%20rally%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CFarmers%20have%20always%20greeted%20each%20other%20with%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3ERam%20Ram%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3ERam%20Ram%20Sa%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%E2%80%99%20or%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3ERam%20Ramji%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99.%20With%20the%20divine%20arrival%20of%20Lord%20Ram%20on%20one%20hand%20and%20the%20recognition%20of%20the%20farmer%E2%80%99s%20leader%2C%20Chaudhary%20Charan%20Singh%2C%20with%20the%20Bharat%20Ratna%20on%20the%20other%2C%20I%20urge%20our%20farmers%20to%20convey%20their%20felicitations%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20speech%20sheds%20light%20on%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20strategy%20in%20the%20region%2C%20highlighting%20four%20major%20issues%20the%20party%20is%20focusing%20in%20Western%20Uttar%20Pradesh%3A%20hindutva%2C%20utilising%20Chaudhary%20Charan%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20legacy%20to%20woo%20Jayant%20and%20farmers%2C%20beneficiary%20schemes%2C%20and%20capitalising%20on%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20popularity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShamshad%20Khan%2C%20psephologist%20and%20managing%20director%20of%20the%C2%A0PEACS%C2%A0news%20service%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CChaudhary%20Charan%20Singh%20commands%20immense%20respect%20in%20the%20region.%20By%20awarding%20him%20the%20Bharat%20Ratna%2C%20the%20BJP%20aims%20to%20accomplish%20two%20objectives%3A%20building%20goodwill%20among%20farmers%20and%20drawing%20RLD%20into%20their%20camp%2C%20thereby%20dealing%20a%20significant%20psychological%20blow%20to%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20and%20SP.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Futtar-pradeshs-economy-down-the-rabbit-hole-and-beyond%5C%22%3EUttar%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20Economy%3A%20Down%20the%20Rabbit%20Hole%20and%20Beyond%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%20the%20BJP%20is%20also%20working%20to%20get%20its%20caste%20equation%20right%20in%20the%20region.%20Laxmi%20Kant%20Bajpai%2C%20BJP%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20from%20Meerut%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CNot%20only%20Jats%2C%20but%20we%20have%20also%20actively%20connected%20with%20numerically%20smaller%20communities%20in%20the%20region%2C%20such%20as%20Tyagis%2C%20Sainis%2C%20Gujjars%2C%20Lohaars%2C%20Kahaars%2C%20and%20Kanchis.%20Moreover%2C%20our%20various%20beneficiary%20schemes%20have%20significantly%20benefited%20these%20groups%2C%20and%20we%20expect%20even%20stronger%20support%20from%20them%20in%20the%20upcoming%20election.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20BSP%20steadily%20losing%20its%20hold%20over%20its%20Dalit%20base%2C%20all%20political%20rivals%20are%20out%20to%20grab%20whatever%20they%20can%20out%20of%20the%20Dalit%20vote.%20And%20BJP%20appears%20to%20be%20way%20ahead%20of%20others%2C%20having%20already%20secured%20a%20substantial%20portion%20of%20Dalit%20voters%20from%20the%20BSP%2C%20the%20party%20is%20continuing%20its%20efforts%20to%20expand%20its%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085