blem%20with%20the%20SP%20is%20that%20they%20were%20too%20dependent%20on%20Jayant%20and%20over%20the%20years%20because%20of%20the%20alliance%20they%20didn%E2%80%99t%20develop%20their%20own%20leaders%20and%20cadre%20in%20the%20region.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20SP%20is%20confident%20about%20countering%20the%20BJP-RLD%20alliance%2C%20Atul%20Pradhan%2C%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20MLA%20from%20Sardhana%2C%20Meerut%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20in%20the%20villages%20are%20unhappy%20about%20RLD%20leaving%20the%20alliance.%20Our%20focus%20on%20issues%20such%20as%20protecting%20the%20Constitution%2C%20speaking%20out%20against%20the%20harassment%20of%20protesting%20farmers%20and%20ensuring%20MSP%20is%20resonating%20strongly%20among%20the%20masses.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F23172935%2FScreen-Shot-2024-02-23-at-5.29.00-PM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22795%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F23172935%2FScreen-Shot-2024-02-23-at-5.29.00-PM.png%20795w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F23172935%2FScreen-Shot-2024-02-23-at-5.29.00-PM-300x174.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-698558%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22462%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EAtul%20Pradhan%20addressing%20a%20gathering.%20Photo%3A%20Atul%20Pradhan%2FInstagram%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAtul%20Pradhan%20presents%20a%20new%20electoral%20strategy%2C%20banking%20on%20the%20support%20from%20Dalit%20voters.%20He%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CA%20significant%20shift%20is%20expected%20in%20west%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20among%20the%20Dalit%20voters.%20Recent%20by-polls%20in%20Mainpuri%2C%20Rampur%2C%20and%20Ghosi%20saw%20strong%20support%20from%20the%20scheduled%20caste%20voters%20for%20the%20SP%20and%20this%20trend%20will%20continue.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBSP%E2%80%99s%20prospects%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMayawati%E2%80%99s%20BSP%2C%20once%20a%20formidable%20force%20in%20the%20western%20region%2C%20has%20seen%20a%20decline%20in%20its%20influence.%20The%20factors%20contributing%20to%20BSP%E2%80%99s%20historical%20strength%20in%20Western%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20included%20the%20significant%20presence%20of%20Dalits%2C%20particularly%20Jatavs%2C%20a%20sub-caste%20to%20which%20Mayawati%20belongs%2C%20alongside%20support%20from%20Muslims%20who%20viewed%20the%20BSP-Jatav%20combination%20as%20a%20winning%20formula.%20Additionally%2C%20BSP%20had%20an%20array%20of%20influential%20leaders%20and%20a%20motivated%20cadre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20political%20commentator%20Ajmal%20Rahi%2C%20who%20also%20runs%20an%20organisation%20for%20communal%20harmony%20in%20Muzaffarnagar%2C%20highlights%20the%20BSP%E2%80%99s%20current%20situation%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20BSP%20is%20almost%20finished%20in%20the%20region%3B%20they%20lack%20major%20issues%2C%20their%20cadres%20have%20weakened%2C%20and%20influential%20leaders%20have%20left%20the%20party.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20BSP%20leaders%20see%20Jayant%E2%80%99s%20departure%20from%20the%20SP%20alliance%20as%20an%20opportunity%20to%20regain%20Muslim%20support%20by%20positioning%20BSP%20as%20the%20main%20alternative%20to%20the%20BJP.%20With%20BSP%E2%80%99s%20Jatav%20base%20remaining%20strong%2C%20the%20alliance%20of%20Jatav%20and%20Muslim%20voters%20could%20pose%20a%20challenge%20to%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahi%C2%A0refutes%20and%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20alliance%20of%20SP%20and%20Congress%20is%20on%20one%20side%2C%20there%20is%20no%20chance%20Muslims%20will%20vote%20for%20Mayawati.%20Muslims%20have%20stopped%20trusting%20Mayawati%20from%20past%20few%20elections%20and%20have%20understood%