cial%20materials%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20continuously%20produced%20at%20an%20amount%20equivalent%20to%20the%20total%20body%20mass%20of%20all%20living%20people.%20This%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20even%20include%20our%20industrial%20pollution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndustrial%20capitalist%20society%20is%20built%20upon%20this%20production%20of%20surplus%20food%2C%20materials%2C%20and%20extra-somatic%20energy%20for%20use%20by%20some%20humans%20more%20than%20others.%20It%20blithely%20presumes%20that%20the%20ecosphere%20will%20readily%20provide%20the%20energy%20and%20materials%20to%20fuel%20this%20overconsumption%20and%20then%20absorb%20the%20mountains%20and%20rivers%20and%20islands%20of%20concomitant%20waste%20and%20pollution%E2%80%94including%20all%20the%20excess%20carbon%20dioxide%20we%20emit.%20The%20cost%20of%20this%20is%E2%80%94as%20it%20has%20always%20been%E2%80%94the%20destruction%20of%20the%20local%20ecosystem%2C%20which%20today%20encompasses%20the%20whole%20planet%2C%20thus%20driving%20the%20mass%20extinction%20of%20non-human%20species%20and%20the%20destruction%20of%20many%20human%20groups%20as%20well.%20The%20result%20is%20a%20biosphere%20critically%20lacking%20in%20biodiversity%2C%20frightfully%20over-polluted%2C%20morbidly%20out%20of%20balance%20and%20overwhelmed%20by%20the%20over-population%20of%20its%20apex%20predator%20species%3A%20humans.%20We%E2%80%99ve%20already%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.stockholmresilience.org%2F5.3d04209a18a2642b2fc162a3.html%5C%22%3Eexceeded%20six%20of%20the%20nine%3C%2Fa%3E%20known%20planetary%20boundaries%20for%20civilizational%20stability.%20Today%20our%20species%20is%20in%20a%20perilous%20state%20of%20ecological%20overshoot.%20Climate%20change%20is%20merely%20one%20symptom%20of%20this%20condition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20are%20strangling%20the%20web%20of%20life%2C%20triggering%20an%20extinction%20event%20such%20as%20our%20planet%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20witnessed%20since%20the%20age%20of%20the%20dinosaurs.%20We%20might%20glean%20from%20this%20the%20same%20fundamental%20lesson%20our%20ancient%20ancestors%20would%20have%20heeded%2C%20when%20they%20were%20not%20so%20separated%20from%20the%20ecological%20feedbacks%20of%20their%20actions.%20Indeed%2C%20some%20communities%20around%20the%20world%20who%20still%20follow%20lifestyles%20much%20more%20closely%20connected%20with%20the%20land%20have%20seen%20the%20signs%20of%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pnas.org%2Fdoi%2F10.1073%2Fpnas.142033699%5C%22%3Eecological%20overshoot%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20have%20tried%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DTq0kWs1q3hI%5C%22%3Ewarn%20us%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpwccc.wordpress.com%2Fsupport%2F%5C%22%3Erepeatedly%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20what%20was%20it%20that%20prompted%20such%20a%20dramatic%20change%20in%20the%20way%20so%20many%20people%20chose%20to%20live%2C%20to%20shift%20from%20immediate-return%20to%20delayed-return%20economies%3F%20From%20socially%20egalitarian%2C%20decentralized%2C%20diverse%20and%20fluidly%20inter-linked%20communities%20to%20deeply%20stratified%2C%20centralized%2C%20relatively%20homogeneous%20and%20bounded%20nation-states%3F%20When%20did%20it%20all%20begin%20to%20change%3F%20Why%3F%20And%20as%20a%20species%2C%20why%20are%20we%20not%20(yet)%20suffering%20population%20decline%20when%20we%20so%20utterly%20despoil%20our%20environment%2C%20as%20our%20ancestors%20suffered%20if%20they%20ruined%20theirs%3F%20The%20answers%20may%20not%20be%20what%20most%20of%20us%20are%20led%20to%20presume.%20I%20will%20attempt%20to%20tease%20them%20out%20in%20the%20forthcoming%20essays%20of%20this%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EUsha%20Alexander%20trained%20in%20science%20and%20anthropology.%20After%20working%20for%20years%20in%20Silicon%20Valley%2C%20she%20now%20lives%20in%20Gurugram.%20She%E2%80%99s%20written%20two%20novels%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3EThe%20Legend%20of%20Virinara%3Cem%3E%C2%A0and%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3EOnly%20the%20Eyes%20Are%20Mine%3Cem%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708843504000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F25113632%2FIMG_2939.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fthe-human-animal-in-the-circle-of-life%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Energy%20and%20materials%20flow%20through%20this%20circle%20of%20life%E2%80%94really%2C%20multiple%20interconnected%20circles%2C%20or%20a%20web%20of%20life%E2%80%94with%20each%20species%20occupying%20its%20place%2C%20or%20niche%2C%20within%20the%20flow.%20But%20now%2C%20humans%20are%20strangling%20the%20web%20of%20life%2C%20triggering%20an%20extinction%20event%20such%20as%20our%20planet%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20witnessed%20since%20the%20age%20of%20the%20dinosaurs.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fthe-human-animal-in-the-circle-of-life%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22900%20Kids%20Are%20Now%20Able%20to%20Hear%2C%20Thanks%20to%20Support%20From%20This%20Life-Changing%20Initiative%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20is%20sponsored%20by%20The%20Hans%20Foundation%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20a%20child%20is%20born%2C%20parents%20celebrate%20each%20milestone%20in%20their%20life%20%E2%80%94%20from%20the%20baby%E2%80%99s%20first%20rollover%20to%20crawling%20and%20walking.%20Another%20significant%20moment%20every%20parent%20eagerly%20awaits%20is%20their%20baby%E2%80%99s%20first%20word.%20Each%20child%20develops%20uniquely%2C%20hitting%20these%20milestones%20at%20different%20times.%20However%2C%20parents%20need%20to%20remain%20attentive%20and%20raise%20concerns%20if%20these%20milestones%20are%20delayed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F334578%2Fcoda-child-of-deaf-adult-indian-sign-language-isl%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHearing%2C%20an%20invisible%20aspect%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20often%20goes%20unnoticed%20until%20the%20child%20begins%20to%20speak%20or%2C%20in%20some%20cases%2C%20doesn%E2%80%99t.%20A%20child%20who%20is%20not%20able%20to%20hear%20won%E2%80%99t%20be%20able%20to%20respond%20to%20noises%20or%20their%20name%2C%20and%20won%E2%80%99t%20start%20babbling%20and%20trying%20to%20imitate%20sounds%20by%20six%20to%20eight%20months.%20If%20parents%20are%20not%20aware%20of%20such%20childhood%20milestones%20they%20may%20not%20become%20aware%20of%20potential%20hearing%20issues%20until%20around%20the%20time%20the%20child%20reaches%20two%20years%20of%20age.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThanks%20to%20advancements%20in%20healthcare%20and%20technology%2C%20newborn%20hearing%20screenings%20can%20now%20detect%20hearing%20loss%20much%20before%20even%20the%20earliest%20milestones-based%20diagnosis.%20These%20screenings%20aid%20in%20the%20early%20detection%20of%20hearing%20problems%2C%20allowing%20for%20follow-up%20consultations%20with%20paediatricians%20within%20the%20baby%E2%80%99s%20first%20two%20to%20three%20months%20of%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20World%20Health%20Organisation%20(WHO)%20estimates%20that%20there%20are%2063%20million%20people%20in%20India%20who%20suffer%20from%20significant%20auditory%20impairment.%20It%20further%20notes%20that%20up%20to%20five%20out%20of%20every%201%2C000%20babies%20are%20born%20with%20hearing%20loss%20or%20acquire%20it%20soon%20after%20birth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20the%20key%20to%20effective%20management%20of%20hearing%20loss%20is%20early%20identification%20and%20prompt%20treatment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChildren%20experiencing%20mild%20to%20moderate%20hearing%20loss%20can%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F63445%2Fhearing-impairments-balavidyalaya-school-chennai%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebenefit%20from%20hearing%20aids%3C%2Fa%3E.%20For%20those%20with%20profound%20hearing%20loss%2C%20Cochlear%20Implants%20(CI)%20offer%20a%20solution.%20These%20electronic%20devices%20serve%20to%20replace%20the%20function%20of%20the%20damaged%20inner%20ear%2C%20facilitating%20the%20sense%20of%20hearing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20enables%20children%20to%20engage%20with%20the%20auditory%20world%20and%20lead%20lives%20similar%20to%20other%20children%20in%20every%20aspect.%20However%2C%20the%20cost%20of%20Cochlear%20Implant%20(CI)%20surgery%20is%20expensive%20for%20a%20large%20portion%20of%20the%20population%20in%20India.%20To%20assist%20children%20in%20regaining%20their%20hearing%20abilities%20and%20leading%20fulfilling%20lives%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F341889%2Fhans-foundation-bal-aarogya-karyakram-childhood-cancer-paediatric-oncology-leukaemia-lymphoma%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Hans%20Foundation%20%3C%2Fa%3E(THF)%20runs%20the%20Cochlear%20Implant%20Programme.%20Through%20this%20initiative%2C%20they%20have%20already%20helped%20over%20900%20children%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20two-hour%20surgery%20that%20can%20change%20lives%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%202560px)%20100vw%2C%202560px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIMG_1342-min-1708783870-scaled.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222560%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Hans%20Foundation%20(THF)%20has%20helped%20over%20900%20children%20with%20its%20Cochlear%20Implant%20Programme.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIMG_1342-min-1708783870-scaled.jpg%202560w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIMG_1342-min-1708783870-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIMG_1342-min-1708783870-500x375.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2