hat%20time%2C%20I%20was%20looking%20for%20ways%20where%20I%20could%20start%20a%20business%20with%20less%20capital%20and%20space.%20One%20day%2C%20one%20of%20my%20friends%20suggested%20I%20try%20my%20hands%20at%20oyster%20pearl%20farming%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20did%20not%20want%20to%20get%20into%20traditional%20farming%20as%20I%20had%20seen%20my%20family%20do%20that%20only%20for%20%3Cem%3Echaumasa%20%3C%2Fem%3E(four%20months%20of%20monsoon)%20and%20then%20switching%20to%20survive%20on%20daily%20wage%20jobs%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FPearl-farming-2-1708607973.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Priced%20at%20Rs%20500%20each%20pearl%2C%20Vinod%20earns%20an%20income%20of%20Rs%2020%20lakh%2C%20which%20is%20thrice%20the%20investment%20amount.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FPearl-farming-2-1708607973.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FPearl-farming-2-1708607973-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FPearl-farming-2-1708607973-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FPearl-farming-2-1708607973-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FPearl-farming-2-1708607973-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-342924%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EPriced%20at%20Rs%20500%20for%20each%20pearl%2C%20Vinod%20earns%20an%20income%20of%20Rs%2020%20lakh%2C%20which%20is%20thrice%20the%20investment%20amount.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20get%20a%20clear%20understanding%20of%20oyster%20pearl%20farming%2C%20Vinod%20went%20to%20Odisha%20%E2%80%93%20about%201%2C700%20km%20from%20his%20village%20in%20Sikar%20district.%20After%20undertaking%20training%20from%20ICAR-Central%20Institute%20of%20Freshwater%20Aquaculture%20(CIFA)%2C%20he%20returned%20to%20his%20village%20with%20500%20oysters%20and%20high%20hopes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVinod%20dug%20a%2010%C3%975%20ft%20pond%20inside%20his%20home%20and%20released%20all%20the%20oysters%20in%20it.%20Sadly%2C%20he%20lost%20453%20oysters%20within%20a%20month.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20failed%20miserably.%20I%20overlooked%20the%20fact%20that%20we%20have%20a%20very%20different%20and%20hot%20environment%20here%20in%20Rajasthan.%20Even%20our%20water%20quality%20is%20different%20from%20the%20coastal%20state%20of%20Odisha.%20I%20also%20made%20a%20few%20mistakes%20in%20preparing%20the%20pond%2C%20and%20also%20while%20giving%20supplements%2C%20checking%20the%20pH%20and%20ammonia%20levels%2C%20and%20performing%20surgeries%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F334671%2Fmaharashtra-farmers-oyster-pearl-cultivation-battle-drought-suicide-earn-income%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DWhen%2520Droughts%2520Led%2520to%2520Losses%252C%2520Oyster%2520Pearl%2520Farming%2520Helped%2520Marathwada%2Cpearl%2520farming%2520to%2520reap%2520profits.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eextract%20pearls%20from%20the%20oysters%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EEarning%20thrice%20the%20inputs%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FPearl-farming-3-1708608002.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Currently%2C%20Vinod%20says%20the%20success%20rate%20of%20oyster%20pearl%20farming%20is%20between%2070%20and%2080%20percent.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FPearl-farming-3-1708608002.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FPearl-farming-3-1708608002-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FPearl-farming-3-1708608002-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FPearl-farming-3-1708608002-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FPearl-farming-3-1708608002-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-342925%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ECurrently%2C%20Vinod%20says%20the%20success%20rate%20of%20oyster%20pearl%20farming%20is%20between%2070%20and%2080%20percent.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVinod%20rectified%20these%20mistakes%20in%20the%20second%20batch.%20He%20bought%20another%201%2C000%20oysters%20and%20released%20them%20in%20the%20pond.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20time%2C%20I%20regularly%20checked%20the%20pH%20and%20the%20temperature%20in%20the%20pond.%20Ideally%2C%20the%20pH%20should%20be%207.5%20%5Bbasic%5D%20and%20the%20temperature%20should%20be%20maintained%20between%2025%20and%2030%20degrees.%20During%20summer%2C%20the%20temperature%20shoots%20to%2050%20degrees%20in%20our%20region.%20To%20maintain%20an%20ideal%20temperature%2C%20I%20installed%20a%20green%20shade%20and%20kept%20rotating%20water%20for%203-4%20hours%20in%20a%20day%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20he%20had%20hoped%2C%20the%20success%20rate%20this%20time%20was%2070%20percent.%20%E2%80%9CWith%20this%2C%20I%20made%20a%20profit%20of%20Rs%2050%2C000%20and%20recovered%20the%20investment%20amounts%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20smiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20Vinod%20used%20the%20profits%20to%20expand%20pearl%20farming%20in%20four%20ponds%20s