ate-career-for-farming-exotic-fruits-vegetables-earns-lakhs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eincreasing%20yield%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%2020%20percent%20while%20cutting%20the%20cost%20by%2050%20percent.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAkshay%20assured%20him%20it%20did.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20gain%20Sahu%E2%80%99s%20trust%2C%20Akshay%20told%20him%20he%20would%20be%20shipping%20him%20one%20tonne%20of%20the%20product%20(20%20bags%20of%20fertiliser)%20for%20free.%20%E2%80%9CYou%20can%20try%20it%20to%20believe%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20Sahu%2C%20who%20was%20thrilled.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20months%20that%20followed%2C%20not%20only%20did%20this%20%E2%80%9Cmiracle%E2%80%9D%20product%20help%20Sahu%E2%80%99s%20paddy%20field%20tremendously%2C%20but%20it%20also%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F342126%2Fhow-to-grow-water-lily-at-home-gardener-viji-abi-shares-easy-tips-thrissur-nymphaea-sree%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eincreased%20productivity%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20neighbouring%20fields%20where%20it%20was%20used.%20In%20total%2C%2015%20farmers%20were%20witness%20to%20the%20wonders%20of%20the%20product.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20difference%20in%20the%20health%20of%20the%20crop%20was%20visible.%20And%20passersby%20were%20quick%20to%20notice.%20Sahu%20would%20tell%20everyone%20who%20enquired%20that%20a%20fertiliser%20was%20responsible%20for%20this%20drastic%20transformation.%20And%20soon%2C%20many%20hopped%20onto%20the%20bandwagon%20of%20wanting%20to%20purchase%20the%20product%2C%20compelling%20Sahu%20to%20start%20an%20outlet%20where%20he%20procured%20and%20sold%20LCB%20Fertilisers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fagriculture-1708603905.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20a