areer-for-farming-exotic-fruits-vegetables-earns-lakhs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20engineer-turned-agriprenuer%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20Nagendra%20Naidu%20Dharmavarapu%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20Farmties%20India%20Private%20Limited.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Nagendra%2C%20it%20is%20important%20to%20find%20one%E2%80%99s%20niche%20in%20farming%20to%20earn%20profits.%20He%20found%20his%20niche%20in%20Yellow%20Dates%2C%20a%20super%20food%2C%20which%20is%20earning%20him%20Rs%203.5%20lakhs%20per%20acre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIntrigued%20by%20the%20product%20and%20how%20he%20found%20his%20market%2C%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20had%20a%20conversation%20with%20Nagendra%20where%20he%20recalls%20his%20initial%20days%20of%20brainstorming%20to%20make%20profits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBack%20to%20his%20roots%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20into%20a%20family%20of%20farmers%2C%20Nagendra%20grew%20up%20in%20close%20proximity%20to%20the%20issues%20farmers%20faced%20on%20a%20daily%20basis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20intimately%20familiar%20with%20these%20challenges%20and%20had%20grown%20up%20pondering%20potential%20solutions.%20In%20my%20mind%2C%20it%20was%20clear%20that%20I%20wanted%20to%20be%20an%20agripreneur%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20while%20Nagendra%20was%20in%20an%20engineering%20college%2C%20he%20would%20frequently%20return%20home%20and%20spend%20time%20on%20the%20farm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20had%20a%20strong%20affinity%20for%20the%20farms%20and%20was%20very%20determined%20that%20one%20day%20I%20would%20also%20transition%20into%20the%20agriculture%20space%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fkavi-4-1708522473.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20al