njoying%20his%20work%2C%20his%20true%20passion%20lay%20in%20farming.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20a%20risk%20that%20I%20was%20taking%20as%20my%20jobs%20were%20very%20high%20paying.%20Leaving%20all%20that%20and%20moving%20into%20a%20familiar%20yet%20unknown%20space%20was%20a%20leap%20of%20faith%20for%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20late%202018%2C%20Nagendra%20was%20already%20looking%20for%20a%20potential%20product%20that%20he%20could%20grow.%20%E2%80%9CI%20did%20not%20have%20to%20look%20anywhere%20for%20farms%20as%20my%20family%20owned%20lands%20near%20Anantapur%20which%20is%20also%20in%20proximity%20to%20Bengaluru%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20only%20issue%20was%20water%20scarcity.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20issue%20too%20was%20solved%20when%20a%20known%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F309314%2Fbengaluru-deep-tech-startup-chara-builds-rare-earth-metal-free-electric-vehicle-motors%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emotor%20company%3C%2Fa%3E%20factory%20opened%20just%20a%20few%20kilometres%20away.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20brought%20water%20to%20the%20area%20and%20also%20became%20a%20tipping%20point%20for%20me.%20I%20was%20now%20sure%20that%20I%20wanted%20to%20utilise%20this%20piece%20of%20land%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFinding%20a%20market%20for%20yellow%20dates%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20moving%20into%20agriculture%2C%20Nagendra%20did%20a%20lot%20of%20groundwork%20visiting%20various%20villages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20were%20a%20lot%20of%20fruits%20such%20as%20papaya%2C%20coconut%2C%20and%20mangoes%20that%20would%20grow%20well%20in%20the%20climatic%20conditions%20but%20I%20did%20not%20want%20to%20enter%20that%20space.%20I%20was%20aware%20that%20the%20government%20gives%20a%20lot%20of%20subsidies%20to%20farmers%20to%20grow%20these.%20This%20makes%20it%20accessible%20to%20everyone%20who%20wa